hadiths[182]{hadithnumber,text}:
7235,"Amr Naqid ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Zenab binte-Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni neend se bedaar huey jabke aap farma rahe they : Allah ke siwa koi sachcha maabood nahi, Arab us shar ki wjah se halaak ho gaey jo qareeb aa pahuncha hai. aaj yaajooj-maajooj ki diwar mein se is qadr jagah khul gaee hai. aur Sufiyan ne apne hath se das (10) ka ishara banaya. (hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : maine kaha : ham mein nek log maujood hongey, phir bhi ham halaak ho jaeinge ? farmaya : haan jab shar aur gandagi zyada ho jaeygi."
7236,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba, Saeed-bin-Amr-ash'ashi, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Sufiyan se bayan ki hui riwayat ki sanad mein mazeed kaha : Zainab-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) taala anhumaa ne Habiba se, unhon-ne Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki."
7237,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke unhein Zainab-binte-abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Hazrat Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anhu) binte-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse bayan kiya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha, aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghabraahat ke aalim mein surkh chehrey ke sath (khuwab gaah se) nikley. aap farma rahe they : Allah ke siwa koi sachcha maabood nahi Arab usi shar ki wjah se halaak ho gaey jo ab qareeb aa pahuncha hai. aaj yaajooj-maajooj ki diwar is qadr khul gaee hai. aur aap ne shahadat ki ungli aur angoothey ko mila kar halqa banaya. (hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : to maine kaha ham mein nek log maujood hon, ya phir bhi ham halaak ho jaeinge , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , jab shar aur gandagi zyada ho jaeygi."
7238,Aqeel-bin-Khalid aur Saleh donon ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se Yunus ki Zohri se hadis ke mutabiq aur usi ki sanad se bayan kiya.
7239,"Ahmed-bin-Ishaq ne kaha : hamein Wuhaib ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Taaus ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu hareer (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj yaajooj-maajooj ki diwar itni khul gaee hai. Wuhaib ne apni ungli se nawwey (90) ka nishan banaya."
7240,"Jarir ne Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-qibtiya se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Haaris-bin-abi-Rabee,  Abdullah-bin-safwaan aur main bhi unke sath tha. ham Ummul-Momenin Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, un donon ne unse us lashkar ke mutaalliq sawal kiya jis ko zamin mein dhansaa diya jaeyga, ye Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) (ki khilafat) ka zamana tha. (Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : aik panah leney wala Baitullah mein panah lega, uski taraf aik lashkar bheja jaeyga, jab wo log zamin ke banjar hamwaar hissey mein hongey to unko zamin mein dhansaa diya jaeyga maine kaha : Allah ke rasool ! jo majbur unke sath (shamil) hoga uska kya baney ga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey bhi unke sath dhansaa diya jaeyga albatta qiyamat ke din usko uski niyat ke mutabiq uthaya jaeyga aur abu-Jafar ne kaha : ye Madina (ke qareeb) ka chatiyal hissey hoga (jahan unko dhansaayaa jaeyga)."
7241,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' ne hamein isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur unki hadis mein hai : (ibne-qibtiya ne) kaha : to main abu-Jafar se mila, maine kaha : unhon ( Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu)) ne to zamin ka aik chatiyal maidan kaha tha. to abu-Jafar ne kaha : hargiz nahi, Allah ki qism ! wo Madina ka chatiyal hissey hai."
7242,"Umayya-bin-safwaan se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne dada abdulla-bin-safwaan ko kehtey huey suna ke mujhey Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : aik lashkar (Allah ke) is ghar ke khilaf jang karne ke liye iska rukh karega yahan tak ke jab wo zamin ke chatiyal hissey mein hongey to unke darmyan waley hissey ko (zameen mein) dhansaa diya jaeyga unmein se aik alehda reh janey waley shakhs ke siwa, jo unke barey mein khabar dega aur koi (zinda) baqi nahi bachey ga. to aik shakhs ne (unki baat sun kar) kaha : main tumharey barey mein gawahi deta hun ke tum ne Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) par jhoot nahi baandha aur main (ye bhi) gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein jhoot nahi kaha."
7243,"Ubaidullaah-bin-Amr ne kaha : hamey Zaid-bin-abi-Unaisa ne Abdul-Malik Aamiri se khabar di, unhon-ne Yoosuf-bin-Maahik se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-safwaan ne Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik qaum is ghar yani Kaba mein panah leygi, unke paas na apna difaa' (bachaw) karne ke liye koi zariya hoga, na adadi quwwat hogi aur na samane-jang hi hoga, unki taraf aik lashkar rawaana kiya jaeyga yahan tak ke jab wo (lashkar ke) log zamin ke aik chatiyal hissey mein hongey to unko (zameen mein) dhansaa diya jaeyga Yusuf (bin-maahik) ne kaha : un dinon ahale-Sham (Syria) Makka ki taraf badhey aa rahe they, to Abdullah-bin-safwaan ne kaha : dekho , Allah ki qism ! ye wo lashkar nahi hai. Zaid (bin-abi-Aneesa) ne kaha : aur mujhey abdul-Malik-Aamiri ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Sabit se, unhon-ne Haaris-bin-abi-Rabee se, unhon-ne Ummul-Momenin (Raziallahu anhu) se, Yoosuf-bin-Maahik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne usmein us lashkar ki baat nahi ki jiska Abdullah-bin-safwaan ne zikr kiya."
7244,"Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne neend ke doran (iztiraab (be-chaini) ke aalim) mein apne hath ko harkat di to ham ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aap ne neend mein kuchh aisa kiya jo pahley aap nahi kiya kartey they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye ajeeb baat hai ke (aakhiri zamaney mein) meri ummat mein se kuchh log Baitullah ki panah leney waley Quraish ke aik aadmi ke khilaf (kaarwaai karne ke liye) Baitullah ka rukh karengey yahan tak ke jab wo chatiyal maidan hissey mein hongey to unhein (zameen mein) dhansaa diya jaeyga. ham ne arz kiya, Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! rasta to har tarah ke logon ke liye hota hai. aap ne farmaya : haan , unmein se koi apni muhim se aagah hoga, koi majbur aur koi musaafir hoga. wo sab ikatthey halaak hongey aur (qiyamat ke roz ( waapsi ke mukhtalif raston par niklengey. Allah unhein unki niyaton ke mutabiq uthaaeyga."
7245,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Urwa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina Munawra ke qil'on mein se aik qil'ey ( unchi mehfooz Imaarat ( par chadhey , phir farmaya : kya tum (bhi) dekhtey ho jo main dekh raha hoon? main tumharey gharon mein fitnon ke waaqe honey ke maqamat barish tapakney ke nishanat ki tarah ( kasrat se aur waazeh ( dekh raha hun."
7246,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7247,"ibne-Musaiyab aur abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : an-qareeb fitney hongey, unmein baitha rehney wala khadey rehney waley se behtar hoga aur unmein khada honey wala chalney waley se behtar hoga aur unmein chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga jo unki taraf jhaankey ga bhi wo usey aundha kar dengey aur jis ko un (ke doran ( mein koi panah gaah mil jaey wo uski panah hasil kar ley."
7248,"Abu-Bakar-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-mutee'-bin Aswad se, unhon-ne naufal-bin-Muawiya se Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki usi hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, albatta Abu-Bakar ne mazeed kaha hai : namazon mein aik Namaz aisi hai jiski wo (namaz ( faut ho gaee to maano uska ahal aur maal (sab kuchh) tabah ho gaya."
7249,"Ibrahim-bin-Sad ke walid ne abu-Salma se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aisa fitna (barpa hoga) jis mein soney wala jaagney waley se behtar hoga aur is mein jaagney wala (uth) khadey ho janey waley se behtar hoga aur is mein khada ho janey wala daudney waley se behtar hoga jis ko bachney ki jagah ya koi panah gaah mil jaey to wo (uski) panah hasil kare."
7250,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Usman shihaam ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aur Farqad sabkhi Muslim-bin-abi-bakra ke yahan gaey, wo apni zamin mein they ham unke yahaan andar dakhil huey aur kaha : kya aap ne apne walid ko fitnon ke barey mein koi hadis bayan kartey huey sunaa? unhon-ne kaha : haan , maine (apne walid (Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ne farmaya : an-qareeb fitney barpa hongey sun lo ! phir (aur) fitney barpa hongey, un (ke dauran) mein betha rehney wala chalney waley se behtar hoga, aur unmein chalney wala daudney waley se behtar hoga yad rakho ! jab wo nazil hoga ya waaqe hongey to jiske ( paas ( oont hon wo apne oonton ke paas chala jaey, jiske paas bakriyan hon wo bakriyon ke paas chala jaey aur jiski zamin ho wo zamin mein chala jaey. (Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to aik shakhs ne kaha Allah ke rasool ! uske barey mein kya khayal hai jiske paas na oont hon, na bakriyan , na zamin ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo apni talwaar ley , uski dhaar ko patthar se kutey (kund kar de) aur phir agar bach sakey to bach nikley ! aey Allah ! kya maine ( haq ( pahuncha diya ? aey Allah ! kya maine ( haq ( pahuncha diya ? aey Allah ! kya maine pahuncha diya ? kaha : to aik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool ! agar mujhey majbur kar diya jaey aur ley ja kar aik saf mein ya aik fareeq ke sath khada kar diya jaey aur koi aadmi mujhey apni talwaar ka nishana bana de ya koi teer aaey aur mujhey mar daley to? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (agar tum ne waar na kiya ho) to wo apne aur tumharey gunah samet ley jaeyga aur ahale-jahannam mein se ho jaeyga."
7251,Wakee aur ibne-abi-Adi ne Usman shihaam se isi sanad ke sath ibne-Adi ki hadis ko Hammad ki hadis ki tarah aakhir tak bayan kiya aur Wakee ki hadis is baat par khatm ho gaee : agar wo bach sakey (to bach jaey) aur baad wala hissey bayan nahi kiya.
7252,"abu-Kamil Fuzail-bin-Husain Jahdari ne mujhey hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub aur Yunus se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ahnaf-bin-Qais se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main (ghar se) us shakhs (hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath shamil honey) ke iraadey se nikla to mujhey Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) miley. unhon-ne puchha : Ahnaf ! kahan ka irada hai? kaha : maine kaha ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha-zaad yani Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki nusrat karna chahta hun. kaha to unhon-ne mujh se kaha : Ahnaf ! lot jao kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha, aap farma rahe they jab do musalman apni-apni talwaaron ke sath aamney samney aa jayen to qaatil aur maqtool donon (jahannam ki) aag mein hongey. kaha : to maine arz kiya ya kaha gaya, Allah ke rasool ! ye to qaatil hua ( lekin) maqtool ka ye haal kyon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is ne (bhi) apne sathi ko qatl karne ka irada kar liya tha."
7253,"Ahmad-bin-Abda zabi ne hamein yahi hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne Ayub Yunus aur Mu-alla-bin-zyada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hasan se unhon-ne ahnaf-bin-Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab do musalman apni-apni talwaaron se aapas mein takraae to qaatil aur maqtool donon aag mein hongey."
7254,Mamar ne hamein Ayub se isi sanad ke sath Hammad se abu-Kamil ki hadis ki tarah aakhir tak bayan kiya.
7255,Rabai-bin-Hirash ne Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab do musalmanon mein se aik ne apne bhai par aslaha kushi ki to wo donon jahannam ke kinarey par hain phir jab unmein se aik ne (mauqa patey) doosrey ko qatl kar diya to donon ikatthey jahannam mein dakhil hongey.
7256,Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat ki kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki unhon-ne kai hadisein zikr ki unmein se (eik ye thi) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat us waqt qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke musalmanon ki do badi jamatein aapas main hi jang karein gi. un donon ke darmyan badi qatl aur ghaaratgari hogi jabke donon aik hi ( baat yani haq ki nusrat ka ( daawa karti hongin.
7257,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke bahut zyada harj ( jaanon ki tabahi (ho jaeygi? unhon ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ( ne puchha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! harj ( tabahi ( kya hogi ? farmaya : qatl , qatl."
7258,"Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se unhon-ne abu-Asma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala ne mere liye zamin ko lapet diya aur maine iske mashaariq aur maghaarib ko dekh liya aur jahan tak ye zamin mere liye lapeti gaee an-qareeb meri ummat ki hukumat wahan tak pahuncheygi. aur mujhey surkh aur safaid donon khazaaney (soney aur chandi ke zakhaayer ( diye gaey aur maine apne rab se apni ummat ke liye ye sawal kiya ke wo usko aam qahat saalii se halaak na karey aur unke alawa se un par koi dushman musallat na karey jo majmooi taur par un sab (ki jaanon ( ko munasib (jayez) kar ley. be-shak mere rab ne farmaya : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! jab main koi faisla kar dun to wo radd nahi hota. bila-shubah maine aap ki ummat ke liye aapko ye baat ata kar di hai ke unko aam qahat saali se halaak nahi karunga aur un par unke alawa se kisi aur dushman ko musallat na karun gaa, jo un sab (ki jaanon ( ko munasib qarar de ley. chahey unke khilaf unke aas-paas waley. ya kaha : unke aas-paas walon ke andar se hon, ikatthey kyon na hon jaaein. yahan tak ke ye ( khud ( aik doosrey ko halaak karengey aur aik doosrey ko qaidi banaaein gey."
7259,Qatada ne abu-Qilaba se unhon-ne abu-Asma Yahya se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak Allah Taala ne zamin ko mere liye lapet diya yahan tak ke maine iske mashaariq aur maghaarib ko dekh liya aur us ne mujhey surkh aur safaid do khazaaney ata farmaey. iske baad abu-Qilaba se Ayub ki riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya.
7260,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Usman-bin-Hakim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid (Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (Madina ke) oopri ilaaqey se tashrif laey yahan tak ke jab aap banu-Muawiya ki masjid ke qareeb se guzrey to aap usmein dakhil huey aur do rakatein ada farmaein. ham ne bhi aap ke sath Namaz padhi aur aap ne apne rab se bahut lambi dua ki phir aap ne hamari taraf rukh kiya to farmaya : maine apne rab se teen (cheezein) maangin. us ne do mujhey ata farma di aur aik mujh se rok li. maine apne rab se ye maanga ke wo meri ( poori ( ummat ko qahat saali se halaak na karey to usne mujhey ye cheez ata farma di aur maine us se maanga ke wo meri ummat ko gharq karke halaak na karey to usne ye (bhi) mujhey ata farma di aur maine us se ye sawal kiya ke unki aapas mein jang na ho to usne ye (baat) mujh se rok li."
7261,"Marwan-bin-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Usman-bin-Hakim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid (Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu)) se khabar di ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ki aik jamat ke sath aaey aur aap banu-Muawiya ki masjid ke qareeb se guzrey. (aagey) ibne-Numair ki hadis ki tarah."
7262,Yunus ne mujhey ibne-Shahab se khabar di ke abu-Idrees Kholani kaha kartey they ke Hazrat Huzaifa-bin-yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya : Allah ki qism ! main ab se lekar qiyamat tak hone-waale tamam fitnon ke barey mein baqi sab logon ki nisbat zyada janta hun aur (unhein bayan karne mein) mere liye iske siwa aur koi ( rukawat ( nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se koi cheez raaz ke taur par mujhey batai thi jo aap ne mere alawa kisi aur ko nahi batai thi. ( aisi baatein main kabhi bayan nahi karunga ( albatta Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik majlis mein jahan main maujood tha fitnon ko shumaar kar rahe they : unmein se teen ( fitney ( aisey hain jo taqriban kisi cheez ko baqi nahi chhodengey aur unmein se kuchh fitney aisey hain jo mausam garmaa ki aandhiyon ki tarah hain unmein kuchh chhotey hain aur kuchh badey hain. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere siwa wo sab log (jo us majlis mein maujood they) rukhsat ho gaey.
7263,Jarir ne Aamash se unhon-ne Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey samney khadey huey aur aap ne apne khadey honey ke us waqt se lekar qiyamat tak honey wali koi ( aham ( baat na chhodi. magar usey bayan farma diya jisne is ( bayan ( ko yad rakha us ne usey yad rakha aur jisne usey bhulaa diya us ne usey bhulaa diya. wo sab kuchh mere un sathiyon ke ilm mein aaya phir unmein se koi cheez pesh aati hai jo main bhool chuka hota hun to jab usey dekhta hun to wo mujhey yad aa jati hai bilkul isi tarah jaisey insan kisi ghayab ho janey waley shakhs ka chehra yad rakhta hai jab usey dekhta hai to pehchan leta hai.
7264,Sufiyan ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath un (Huzaifa (Raziallahu anhu)) ke us qaul tak : aur jisne usey bhulaa diya us ne usey bhulaa diya riwayat ki aur uske baad ka hissa bayan nahi kiya.
7265,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adi-bin-Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Yazeed se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qiyamat qaaim honey tak jo kuchh honey wala hai uski mujhey khabar di aur unmein se koi cheez nahi magar maine aap se iske barey mein sawal kiya albatta maine aap se ye sawal nahi kiya ke ahale-Madina ko Madina se kon si cheez bahar nikaley gi."
7266,Wahab-bin-Jareer ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7267,ilbaa-bin-Ahmar ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Zai- Amr-bin-akhtab (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bayan kiya kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein fajr ki Namaz padhai aur member par raunaq afroz huey to hamein khutba diya yahan tak ke Zohar ki Namaz ka waqt ho gaya. aap (member se) utrey hamein Namaz padhai phir dobara member par raunaq afroz huey aur (aagey) khutba irshad farmaya : yahan tak ke Asr ki Namaz ka waqt ho gaya phir aap utrey Namaz padhai aur phir member par tashrif le gaey aur khutba diya yahan tak ke suraj ghurub ho gaya. aap ne jo kuchh hua aur jo honey wala tha (sab) hamein bata diya ham mein se zyada jaanney wala wahi hai jo yad-daasht mein dusron se badh kar hai.
7268,"abu-Muawiya ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne (abu-Waail) Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they ke unhon-ne kaha : fitney ke mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka irshad jis tarah aap ne khud farmaya tha tum mein se kisi ko yad hai? (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine kaha : mujhey.  (hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : tum bahut jur'at mand ho. (ye bataao ke) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kis tarah irshad farmaya tha? maine kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha aap farma rahe they. insan apne ghar walon, apne maal, apni jaan aur apne hamsaaey ke barey mein jis fitney mein mubtala hota hai to roza, Namaz , sadqa , neki ka hukm karna aur burai se mana karna uska kaffara bin jatey hain. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : meri murad us se nahi meri murad to us ( fitney ( se hai jo samandar ki maujon ki tarah umad kar aata hai. Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ameerul-momenin ! aapko us fitney se kiya ( khatrah ( hai? aap ke aur us fitney ke darmyan aik band darwaza hai. unhon-ne kaha : wo darwaza todaa jaeyga ya khola jaeyga? kaha : maine jawab diya nahi balke todaa jaeyga (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir is baat ki zyada tawaqqo hai ke wo ( darwaza dobara ( kabhi band nahi kiya ja sakega. (Shaqeeq ne) kaha : ham ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) jantey they ke darwaza kon hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan isi tarah jaisey wo ye baat jantey they ke subah ke baad raat hai maine unko aik hadis bayan ki thi wo koi atkal pachchu baat na thi. kaha : phir ham is baat se dar gaey ke Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochhein wo darwaza kon tha? ham ne Masruq se kaha : aap un (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu)) se poochhein unhon-ne puchha to (Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : (wo darwaza (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) (they)."
7269,"Wakee , Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus aur Yahya-bin-Esa sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath abu-Muawiya ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur Shaqiq se Aamash aur unse Esa ki hadis mein ye ( jumla ( hai kaha : maine Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna."
7270,"ibne-abi-Umar ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne jaame-bin-abi-Rashid se aur Aamash ne abu-Waail (Shaqeeq) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kon hai jo hamein fitney ke barey mein hadis bayan karega? aur (phir) un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7271,"Muhammad (bin-Sirin) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main jura'a ke din wahan aaya to ( wahan ( aik shakhs betha hua tha. maine kaha : aaj yahan bahut khoonrezi hogi. us shakhs ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! hargiz nahi hogi. maine kaha : Allah ki qism ! zaroor hogi usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! hargiz nahi hogi, maine kaha Allah ki qism ! zaroor hogi usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! hargiz nahi hogi, ye Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis hai jo aap ne mujhey irshad farmai thi. maine jawab mein kaha : aaj tum mere liye aaj ke bad-tareen sathi ( Sabit huey) ho. tum mujh se sun rahe ho ke main tumhari mukhalifat kar raha hun aur tum ne jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai uski bina par mujhey roktey nahi? phir maine kaha : ye ghussa kaisa? chunanche main ( theek tarah se) unki taraf mutwajjeh hua aur unke barey mein puchha to wo aadmi Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) they."
7272,"Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman al-qaari ne hamein Suhel se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat nahi aaeygi. yahan tak ke dariyaaey Faraat soney ke aik pahaad ko zahir karega. is par (ladtey huey) har sau mein se ninyaanwe log maarey jaeinge aur un (ladney walon) mein se har koi kahega. shayad main hi bach jaaunga. (aur sarey soney ka Malik bin jaaunga.)"
7273,Rooh ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath usi ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki aur mazeed kaha : to mere walid ne kaha : agar tum us pahaad ko dekh lo to uske qareeb bhi mat jaanaa.
7274,Hafs-bin-Aasim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : an-qareeb dariyaaey-Faraat soney ke aik khazaaney ko zahir kar dega jo shakhs wahan maujood ho to wo usmein se kuchh bhi na ley.
7275,"Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : an-qareeb dariyaaey-Faraat soney ke aik pahaad ko zahir kar dega. jo shakhs wahan maujood ho wo usmein se kuchh na ley."
7276,"abu-Kamil Fuzail-bin-Husain aur abu-Ma'n Raqashi ne hamein hadis bayan ki. alfaz abu-Ma'n ke hain. donon ne kaha : hamein Khalid-bin-Haaris ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abdul-hameed-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere walid ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se khabar di, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Haaris-bin-naufal se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khada tha to unhon-ne kaha : duniya ki talab mein logon ki gardanein musalsal aik doosrey se mukhtalif (aur baahami (aapsi) jhagdey aur adaawatein (dushmaniyan) jari ( rahen gi. maine kaha : haan ( bilkul aisey hi hoga ( unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : (wo waqt) qareeb hai ke dariyaaey Faraat soney ke aik pahaad ko zahir karega . jab log iske barey mein sunein gey to uski taraf chal niklengey. jo log us (pahaad) ke qareeb hongey wo kahengey. agar ham ne (doosrey) logon ko usmein se (sona) ley janey ki ijazat de di to wo sab ka sab ley jaeinge kaha : wo is par jang karein-gey to har sau mein se ninyaanwe qatl ho jaengey. abu-Kamil ne apni hadis mein (is tarah) kaha : unhon-ne kaha : main aur Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) qil'a Hassan ke saaey mein thahrey huey they."
7277,"Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (main dekh raha hun ke) Iraq ne apne dirham aur qafeez ko rok liya hai. aur Sham (Syria) ne apna mud aur Dinar rok liya hai. aur misr ne apna irdab aur Dinar rok liya hai. aur tum wahin pahunch gaey ho jahan se tumhari shuruat thi. aur tum wahin pahunch gaey ho jahan se tumhari shuruat thi. aur tum wahin pahunch gaey ho jahan se tumhari shuruat thi. is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ka gosht aur khoon gawah hai."
7278,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke roomi (isai) aa'maaq (Sham (Syria)) mein halb aur antaakiya ke darmyan aik hara-bhara ilaqa jo daabiq Shahar se laga hua hai) ya daabiq mein utrein gey. unke sath muqaabley ke liye (dimashq) Shahar se (ya Madina se) us waqt poori zamin ke behtreen logon ka aik lashkar rawaana hoga jab wo (dushman ke samney) saf mein aa jaygey to roomi (isai) kahengey tum hamarey aur un logon ke darmyan se hat jao jinhoney hamarey logon ko qaidi banaya hua hai ham unse ladein gey to musalman kahengey. Allah ki qism ! nahi ham tumharey aur apne bhaiyon ke darmyan se nahi hatein gey. chunanche wo un (isaiyon) se jang karengey. un (musalmanon) mein se aik tehai shikast taslim kar lengey Allah unki tauba kabhi qabool nahi farmaeyga aur aik tehai qatl kar diye jaengey. wo Allah ke nazdeek afzal tareen shohdaa hongey aur aik tehai fateh hasil karengey. wo kabhi fitney mein mubtala nahi hongey. (hamesha Sabit qadam raheingey) aur Qustuntuniya ko (dobara) fateh karengey. (phir) jab wo ghaneematein taqseem kar rahe hongey aur apne hathiyar unhon-ne Zaitoon ke darakhton se latkaey huey hongey to shaitan unke darmyan cheekh kar elaan karega . Masih (dajjal) tumharey peechhey tumharey ghar walon tak pahunch chuka hai wo nikal padein gey magar ye jhoot hoga. jab wo Sham (Syria) (dimashq) pahunchein gey. to wo namudaar ho jaeyga us dauran mein jab wo jang ke liye taiyaari kar rahe hongey. safein seedhi kar rahe hongey to Namaz ke liye iqamat kahi jaeygi us waqt Hazrat Esa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) utrein gey to unka rukh karengey phir jab Allah ka dushman (dajjal) unko dekhega to is tarah pighley ga jis tarah namak pani mein pighaltaa hai. agar wo (Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) ( usey chhod bhi dein to wo pighal kar halaak ho jaeyga lekin Allah Taala usey un (Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) (ke hath se qatl kiraaey ga aur logon ko unke hathiyar par iska khoon dikhaaey ga."
7279,"Musa-bin-Ali ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat mustaurid qarshi (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ke samney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : qiyamat aaeygi to roomi (isai) logon mein sabse zyada hongey. Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : dekh lo tum kya keh rahe ho? unhon-ne kaha : main wahi keh raha hun jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. (Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : agar tum ne ye kaha hai to unmein char khaslatein hain wo aazmaish ke waqt sab logon se zyada burd-baar hain aur museebat ke baad sab logon ki nisbat jald us se sanbhaltey hain aur peechhey hatney ke baad sab logon ki nisbat jald dobara hamla kartey hain aur miskeenon, yatimon aur kamzoron ke liye sab logon ki nisbat behtar hain aur paanchwein khaslat bahut achi aur khoobsurat hai wo sab logon se badh kar baadshaahon ke zulm ko rokney waley hain."
7280,abdul kareem-bin-Haaris ne abu Shureh ko hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat mustaurid qarshi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : qiyamat aaeygii to roomi ( isai ( logon mein sabse zyada hongey. kaha : Hazrat Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye khabar pahunchi to unhon-ne unse kaha : ye kaisi hadisein hain jo tumhari taraf se bayan ki ja rahi hain. ke tum unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey ho? Hazrat mustaurid qarshi (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine wahi kuchh kaha jo maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. ( mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha ke Hazrat Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar tum ye keh rahe ho (to suno ! ( yaqinan wo aazmaish ke waqt sab logon se badh kar burdbaar hain museebat pesh aaney par sab logon se zyada sakht jaan hain aur apne miskinon aur kamzoron ke haq mein sab logon ki nisbat behtar hain.
7281,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Ali-bin-hijr ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne ibne-Ulaih se riwayat ki. aur alfaz ibne-hijr ke hain. kaha : hamein Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Bilal se, unhon-ne abu-Qatada adwi se aur unhon-ne yaseer-bin-Jaabir se riwayat ki kaha : aik martaba Kufa mein surkh aandhi aai to aik shakhs aaya uska takiya kalam hi ye tha. Abdullah-bin-Masood ! qiyamat aa gaee hai. wo ( Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) tek lagaey huey they (ye baat suntey hi) uth kar baith gaey, phir kehney lagey. qiyamat nahi aaeygi. yahan tak ke na meeraas ki taqseem hogi na ghaneemat hasil honey ki khushi phir unhon-ne is tarah hath se ishara kiya aur iska rukh Sham (Syria) ki taraf kiya aur kaha : dushman (ghair Muslim) ahale-Islam ke khilaf ikatthey ho jaeinge aur ahale-Islam unke (muqaabley ke) liye ikatthey ho jaengey. maine kaha : aap ki murad roomiyon (isaiyon) se hai? unhon-ne kaha : haan, phir kaha : tumhari us jang ke zamaney mein bahut zyada palat-palat kar hamley hongey. musalman maut ki shart qabool karne waley dastey aagey bhejein gey ke wo ghalba hasil kiye baghair wapas nahi hongey. (wahin apni jaanein de dengey.) phir wo sab jang karengey. yahan tak ke raat darmyan mein haail ho jaeygi. ye log bhi wapas ho jaeinge aur wo bhi. donon (main se kisi) ko ghalba hasil nahi hoga aur (maut ki) shart par janey waley sab khatm ho jaengey. phir musalman maut ki shart par (janey waley doosrey) dastey ko aagey karengey ke wo ghalib aaey baghair wapas nahi aaeingey phir (donon fareeq) jang karengey. yahan tak ke unke darmyan raat haail ho jaeygi. ye bhi wapas ho jayenge aur wo bhi koi bhi ghalib nahi (aaya) hoga aur maut ki shart par janey waley khatm ho jaengey. phir musalman maut ke talabgaaron ka dasta aagey karengey aur Sham (Syria) tak jang karengey, phir ye bhi wapas ho jaeinge aur wo bhi koi bhi ghalib nahi ( aaya ( hoga aur maut ke talabgaar khatm ho jaengey. jab chautha din hoga to baqi tamam ahale-Islam unke khilaf uthein gey , Allah Taala (jang ke) chakkar ko un (kaafiron) ke khilaf kar dega. wo sakht khoonrez jang karengey. unhon-ne ya to ye alfaz kahey. uski misal nahi dekhi jaeygi. yahan tak ke parinda unke pahluon se guzrey gaa wo unse jun-hi guzrey ga mar kar gir jaeyga ( hawa bhi itni zehril ho jaeygi.) aik bap ki aulad apni ginti karegi , jo sau they, to unmein se aik ke siwa koi na bacha hoga. (ab) wo kis ghaneemat par khush hongey aur kaisa wirsa (kin waarison mein) taqseem karengey. wo usi haalat mein hongey ke aik (nai) museebat ke barey mein sunein gey . jo us se bhi badi hogi. un tak ye zordaar pukar pahuncheygi. ke dajjal unke peechhey unke baal bachchon tak pahunch gaya hai. unke hathon mein jo hoga. sab kuchh phenk dengey aur tezi se aaeingey aur das jaasus shehsawaar aagey bhejeingey, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main unke aur unke baap-dada ke naam aur unke ghodon (sawaariyon) ke rang tak pehchanta hun. wo us waqt poori zamin par behtreen shehsawaar hongey. ya (farmaya :) poori zamin ke behtreen shehsawaaron mein se hongey. ibne-Abi-Sheba ne apni riwayat mein (yaseer ke bajaey) kaha : aseer-bin-Jaabir se marwi hai."
7282,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Hilal se, unhon-ne abu-Qatada se aur unhon-ne yousair-bin-Jaabir se riwayat ki, kaha : main Hazrat ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas tha ke surkh aandhi aai , phir usi ke mutabiq hadis bayan ki, albatta ibne-Ulaih ki riwayat mukammal aur sair hasil hai."
7283,"Sheban-bin-Farukh ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin-Mugheera ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Humaid-bin-Hilal ne abu-Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne aseer-bin-Jaabir se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar mein they jabke ghar bharaa hua tha. kaha is waqt Kufa mein surkh aandhi chali , phir ibne-Ulaih ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki."
7284,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Naafe-bin-utba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham aik jihad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas kuchh log maghrib ki taraf se aaey jo oon ke kapdey pahney huey they. wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik teeley ke paas aa kar miley. wo log khadey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baithey huey they. mere dil ne kaha ke to chal aur un logon aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan mein ja kar khada ho, aisa na ho ke ye log faraib se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mar daalein. phir mere dil ne kaha ke shayad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chupkey se kuchh baatein unse kartey hon (aur mera jana Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko na-gawar guzrey). phir main gaya aur un logon ke aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan mein khada ho gaya. to maine us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se char baatein yad kin, jinko main apne hath par gintaa hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum pahley to Arab ke jazeere mein (kaafiron se) jihad karogey, Allah Taala usko fateh kar dega. phir Faaris (Iraan) se jihad karogey, Allah Taala is par bhi fateh kar dega phir nasara se lado gey Rome (mojooda Itly) walon se, Allah Taala Rome (mojooda Itly) ko bhi fateh kar dega. phir dajjal se lado gey aur Allah Taala usko bhi fateh kar dega (ye hadis Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka bada moa'jza hai). Naafe (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke aey Jaabir-bin-Samra ! ham samajhtey hain ke dajjal Rome (mojooda Itly) fateh honey ke baad hi niklega."
7285,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Furaat qazaz se, unhon-ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzaifa-bin-Usaid Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas aaey aur ham baatein kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum kya baatein kar rahe ho? ham ne kaha ke qiyamat ka zikr kartey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat qaaim na hogi jab tak ke das nishaniyan us se pahley nahi dekh logey . phir zikr kiya dhooein ka, dajjal ka, zamin ke janwar ka, suraj ke maghrib se nikalney ka, Esa (Alaihissalam) ke utarney ka, yaajooj-maajooj ke nikalney ka, teen jagah khasf ka yani zamin ka dhansnaa aik mashriq mein, doosrey maghrib mein, teesrey jazeera Arab mein aur un sab nishaniyon ke baad aik aag paida hogi jo Yaman se niklegi aur logon ko haankti hui unke (maidan) mahshar ki taraf ley jaeygi."
7286,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz Anbari ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Furaat-Qazzaz se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Tufail se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-sareeha-Huzaifa-bin-Usaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baala khaney mein they aur ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nichey ki taraf baithey huey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamari taraf jhank kar dekha aur farmaya : tum kis baat ka zikr kar rahe ho? ham ne kaha qiyamat ka. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tak das nishaniyan zahir nahi hongi, qiyamat nahi aaeygi : mashriq mein zamin ka dhansnaa , maghrib mein zamin ka dhansnaa aur jazeera Arab mein zamin ka dhansnaa , dhuaan , dajjal , zamin ka chaupaaya , yaajooj-maajooj , maghrib se suraj ka tuloo hona aur aik aag jo adn ke aakhiri kinarey se niklegi aur logon ko haankey gi. Shoba ne kaha : Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' ne mujhey bhi abu-Tufail se aur unhon-ne abu-Sareeha (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr nahi kiya (mauqoof hadis bayan ki) aur (mujhey hadis sunaney waley Furaat aur Abdul-Azeez ( donon mein se aik ne dasween (nishani) ke barey mein kaha : Esa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ka nuzool aur doosrey ne kaha : aik hawa (aandhi) hogi jo logon ko samandar mein phainkey gi."
7287,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Furaat se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat abu-sareeha (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna : unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baala khaney mein they aur ham uske nichey baatein kar rahe they, aur) aagey ( usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki. Shoba ne kaha : aur mera khayal hai (ke Furaat ne) kaha : wo jab qiyam ke liye rukein gey to wo ( aag ( bhi unke sath ruk jaeygi aur jab wo do-pahar ko aaraam karengey to wo bhi unke sath sukoon pazeer ho jaeygi. Shoba ne kaha : mujhey kisi shakhs ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-sareeha (Raziallahu anhu) se yahi hadis bayan ki aur usey marfoo bayan nahi kiya. kaha : un donon ( kisi shakhs aur Furaat Qazzaz ( mein se aik ne kaha : Esa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ka nuzool aur doosrey ne kaha : hua jo unhein samandar mein laa-daley gi."
7288,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne bhi hamein yahi ( hadis) bayan ki, kaha : abu-Nauman hukm-bin-Abdullah ajli ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : Shoba ne hamein Furaat se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo Hazrat abu-Sareeha (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they, kaha : ham baatein kar rahe they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uper se jhank kar hamein dekha. (iske baad) Muaz aur ibne-Jafar ki hadis hai. ibne-Musanna ne kaha : hamein abu-Nauman hukm-bin-Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-sareeha (Raziallahu anhu) se isi tarah riwayat ki, kaha : dasween (alamat) Hazrat Esa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ka nuzool hai. Shoba ne kaha : Abdul-Azeez ne usey mar faua' bayan nahi kiya."
7289,"Yunus aur Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ibne-Musaiyab ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi yahan tak ke arz (zameen) hijaaz se aik aag niklegi jo (Sham (Syria) ke Shahar ( Basri mein oonton ki gardanon ko roshan kar degi."
7290,"Aswad-bin-Aamir ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zuhair ne Suhail-bin-abi-Saleh se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (Madina Munawra ke) ghar ihaab ya yahaab (ke maqam tak) pahunch jaengey. Zuhair ne kaha : maine Suhel se puchha : ye jagah Madina se kitney faasley par hai? unhon-ne kaha : itney-itney meel hai."
7291,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qahat ye nahi hai ke tum par barish na ho balke qahat ye hai ke barish ho, phir barish ho lekin zamin koi cheez na ugaaey."
7292,"Leis ne hamein Naafe se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna jabke aap mashriq ka rukh kiye huey farma rahe they : suno ! fitna yahan hoga, suno ! yahan hoga jahan se shaitan ka seeng namudaar hota hai."
7293,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar qawaareeri, Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur Ubaidullah-bin-Saeed ne hamein hadis bayan ki, un sab ne Yahya (bin-Saeed ( qattaan se riwayat ki, qawaareeri ne kaha : mujhey Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Ubaidullah-bin-Umar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Naafe ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke darwazey ke paas khadey hath se mashriq ki taraf ishara kartey huey farma rahe they : fitna us samt mein hoga jahan se shaitan ka seeng namudaar hota hai. ye baat aap ne do ya teen baar irshad farmai. Ubaidullah-bin-Saeed ne apni riwayat mein kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke darwazey ke paas khadey they."
7294,"ibne-Shahab ne Saalim-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jabke aap ne mashriq ki taraf rukh kiya hua tha : yad rakho ! fitna yahan hai, yad rakho ! fitna yahan hai, yad rakho ! fitna yahan hai, jahan se shaitan ka seeng namudaar hota hai."
7295,"Ikrima-bin-Ammar ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar se bahar tashrif laey aur farmaya : kufr ka sar idhar se zahir hoga jahan se shaitan ka seeng namudaar hota hai. aap ki murad mashriq (ki simt) se thi."
7296,"Hanzala ne kaha : maine Salim se suna, wo kehtey hain : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko mashriq ki taraf hath se ishara karke farmatey huey suna : yad rakho ! fitna us taraf se hai. yad rakho ! fitna usi taraf se hai. teen baar ( farmaya ( jahan se shaitan ka seeng tuloo hota hai. aap ki murad mashriq (ki samt ( se thi."
7297,"Abdullah-bin-Umar-bin-Abaan , Wasil-bin-Abdul-Aala aur Ahmed-bin-Umar-wakee ne hamein hadis bayan ki, alfaz ibne- Aban ke hain. unhon-ne kaha : hamein ibne-Fuzail ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se suna, keh rahe they : aey Iraq waalo ! main tum se chhotey gunah nahi poochhta na usko poochhta hun jo kabeera gunah karta ho maine apne walid saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey they ke fitna idhar se aayega aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se mashriq ki taraf ishara kiya. jahan shaitan ke donon seeng nikaltey hain. aur tum aik doosrey ki gardan maartey ho (halanke momin ki gardan maarna kitna bada gunah hai) aur Musa (Alaihissalam) firaun ki qaum ka aik shakhs ghalati se mar baithey they (na ke baa-niyat qatl kyonke ghoonsey se aadmi nahi martaa), to is par Allah Taala ne farmaya ke '' tu ney aik khoon kiya, phir ham ne tujhey gham se nijat di aur tujh ko aazmaya jaisa aazmaya tha.''"
7298,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat nahi aaeygi yahan tak ke dos ki aurton ke peeth (peethein) , zul-khalasa ke ird-gird (dorane-tawaaf) matkeen gi. wo (zul-khalasa) tabaadla mein aik but tha, jaahili daur mein qabila dos uski puja kiya karta tha."
7299,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abdul-hameed-bin-Jafar ne Aswad-bin-Alaa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Salma se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke raat aur din us waqt tak khatm na hongey jab tak laat aur uzzaa ( jahiliyat ke but ( phir na poojey jaengey. maine arz kiya ke ya Rasulullah ! main to samajhti thi ke jab Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari ''Allah wo hai jisne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hidayat aur sachcha Deen de kar bheja taake usko sab dinon par ghalib karey agarche mushrik log bura maanein.'' ke ye wada pura honey wala hai (aur Islam ke siwa aur koi Deen ghalib na rahega). Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tak Allah Taala ko manzoor hoga, aisa hi hoga. phir Allah Taala aik pakeeza hawa bhejeyga ke jis se har momin mar jaeyga, yahan tak ke har wo shakhs bhi jiske dil mein daney ke barabar bhi imaan hai aur wo log baqi reh jaeinge jin mein bhalai nahi hogi. phir wo log apne ( mushrik ( bap dada ke Deen par lot jaengey."
7300,Abu-Bakar hanfi ne kaha : hamein abdul-hameed-bin-Jafar ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7301,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke aik shakhs doosrey aadmi ki qabr ke paas se guzrey ga to kahega : kash! ! uski jagah main hota."
7302,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! duniya us waqt tak rukhsat nahi hogi, yahan tak ke aik shakhs ( kisi ki) qabr ke paas se guzrey to is par lot-pot hoga aur kahega : kaash! ! us qabr waley ki jagah main hota aur uske paas Deen nahi hoga, bas aazmaish hogi."
7303,"ibne-abi-Umar-Makki ne hamein ye hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Marwan ne Yazeed se. aur wo ibne-kaisaan hai. hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! logon par aik aisa zamana aayega ke qaatil ko pata nahi hoga ke usne kyon qatl kiya aur na maqtool ko pata hoga ke usey kis baat par qatl kiya gaya."
7304,"Abdullah-bin-Umar-bin-Abaan aur Wasil-bin-Abdul-Aala ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Fuzail ne abu-Ismail Aslami se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! duniya khatm nahi hogi yahan tak ke logon par aisa din aa jaey jis mein qaatil ko ye malum na ho ke usne kyon qatl kiya aur maqtool ko ye pata na ho ke usey kyon qatl kiya gaya. kaha gaya ye kaisey hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : andha-dhund khoonrezi hogi, qaatil aur maqtool donon (jahannam ki) aag mein jaengey. ibne-Abaan ki riwayat mein (is tarah) hai : kaha : wo Yazeed-bin-kaisaan hai) jiske barey mein kaha gaya hai) abu-Ismail se riwayat hai) iska pura naam abu Ismail-Yazeed-bin-kaisaan hai) unhon-ne (uski nisbat) Aslami ka zikr nahi kiya."
7305,"Ziyad-bin-Sad ne Zohri se aur unhon-ne Saeed (bin-Musaiyab) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai : Kaba ko Habsha se (talluq rakhney wala) do chhoti-chhoti pindliyon wala shakhs giraaey ga."
7306,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne ibne-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do chhoti-chhoti pindliyon wala habshi Kaba ko giraaey ga ."
7307,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne hamein Abdul-Azeez daraawri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne soor-bin-Zaid se unhon-ne abu-ghais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Habsha ka do chhoti-chhoti pindliyon wala shakhs izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ke ghar ko giraaey ga ."
7308,Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne isi sanad se Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke qahtaan ka aik shakhs logon ko apni laathi se haankey ga.
7309,"abdul kabeer-bin-Abdul-Jabbar Abu-Bakar Hanafi ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein abdul-Hameed-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Umar-bin-hukm ko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : din aur raat ka silsila khatm nahi hoga. yahan tak ke aik shakhs badshah banega . jisey jah'jaah kaha jaeyga. Imam Muslim (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne (abdul-kabeer ke hawale se) kaha : ye char bhai hain. Sharik, Ubaidullah, Umer aur abdul-kabeeriya Abdul-Majeed ke betey hain."
7310,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed (bin-Musaiyab) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke tum aik aisi qaum se jang karogey. jinke chehrey kooti hui dhaalon ki tarah hongey aur qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi. yahan tak ke tum aisi qaum se jang karogey jinke jootey baalon (oon) ke hongey."
7311,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi. yahan tak ke tum aik aisi ummat se jang karogey jo baalon ke jootey pahntey hongey aur unke chehrey kooti hui dhaalon ki tarah hongey."
7312,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne us (ki sanad) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi. yahan tak ke tum us qaum se jang karogey jinke jootey baalon ke hongey aur qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke tum chhoti aankhon aur chhoti naak wali qaum se jang karogey.
7313,Suhel ke walid (Abu-Saleh) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi. yahan tak ke musalman turkon se jang karengey ye aisi qaum hai jinke chehrey kooti hui dhaalon ki tarah hongey. ye log baalon ka libaas pahntey hongey. baalon (ke jooton) mein chaltey hongey.
7314,"Qais-bin-abi-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat se pahley tum aisi qaum se jang karogey. jinke jootey baalon ke hongey. unke chehrey kooti hui dhaalon ki tarah hongey wo surkh chehron aur chhoti aankhon waley hongey."
7315,Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne hamein Jurairi se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne abu-Nazara se riwayat ki kaha : ham Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they ke unhon-ne kaha : wo waqt qareeb hai ke Iraq walon ke paas koi qafeez (paimaana) aaey-gaa na dirham. ham ne puchha kahan se? unhon-ne kaha : ajam se. wo usko rok lengey. phir kaha : an-qareeb ahale-Sham (Syria) ke paas koi Dinar aayega na mud ( paimaana ( ham ne puchha : kahan se ? unhon-ne kaha : Rome (mojooda Itly) ki taraf se phir thodi der khamosh rehney ke baad kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat ke aakhir (ke door) mein aik khaleefa hoga jo lapein bhar-bhar ke maal dega aur uski ginti nahi karega. (Jurairi ne) kaha : maine abu-Nazara aur abu-alaa se puchha : kya aap samajhtey hain ke ye Umar-bin-Abdul-Azeez hain? to donon ne kaha : nahi.
7316,Abdul Wahab ne kaha : hamein Saeed Jarir ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7317,"Nasar-bin-Ali jahazmi ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Bashar-bin-Mufazzal ne hadis bayan ki isi ke saath hamein Ali-bin-Hujr Sadi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ismail-bin-Ulaih ne hadis bayan ki donon ( bashar-bin-Mufazzal aur ibne-Ulaih) ne Saeed-bin-yazeed se unhon-ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed ( Khudri (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumharey khulfaa mein se aik khaleefa hoga jo lapein bhar-bhar kar maal dega aur usko shumaar nahi karega aur (Ali) bin-hijr ki riwayat main ( يَحْثُو الْمَالَ (ke bajaey ( يحثي المال ( hai) mana aik hi hai)."
7318,"Abdus-Samad-bin-Abdul Waris ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Dawud ne abu-Nazara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, donon ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aakhiri zamaney mein aik khaleefa hoga jo maal taqseem karega aur usko shumaar nahi karega."
7319,aur abu-Muawiya ne Dawood-bin-abi-hindsey unhon-ne abu-Nazara se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7320,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Muslima se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Nazara se suna, wo Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they unhon-ne kaha : aik aisey shakhs ne mujhey bataya jo mujh se behtar hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, jab aap ne khandaq khodney ki shuruat ki to Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se aik baat irshad farmai, aap unke sar par hath pherney aur farmaney lagey.Sumayya ke betey ki museebat ! tumhen aik baaghi giroh qatl karega."
7321,"aur Khalid-bin-Haaris aur Nazar-bin-Shumail donon ne Shoba se riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Muslima se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki, albatta nazar ki hadis mein hai. mujhey mujh se behtar shakhs abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di aur Khalid-bin-Haaris ki hadis mein hai ke unhon-ne kaha : mera khayal hai unki murad abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) se thi aur Khalid ki hadis mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaney lagey. afsos ! ya farmaya waay afsos ibne-Sumayya par !"
7322,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ghandar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Khalid hazza ko Saeed-bin-abul-hasan se hadis riwayat kartey huey suna, unhon-ne apni walida se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : tumhen aik baaghi giroh qatl karega."
7323,"Abdus-Samad-bin-Abdul-Waris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Khalid Haza ne Saeed-bin-abi-Hasan aur Hasan se hadis bayan ki un donon ne apni walida se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
7324,"Ibne-Aun ne Hasan se unhon-ne apni walida se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ammar ko aik baaghi giroh qatl karega."
7325,"abu-Usama ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Tayyah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Zura se suna, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : meri ummat ko Quraish ka ye qabila halaak karega. unhon-ne ( sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne arz ki, phir aap hamein kya (karne ka ( hukm detey hain? aap ne farmaya : kaash! ! log unse alag ho jaaein."
7326,Abu-Dawud ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana riwayat ki.
7327,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kisraa mar gaya to uske baad koi Kisraa nahi hoga aur jab qaisar mar jaeyga to uske baad (Sham (Syria) mein) koi qaisar nahi hoga, us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! un donon ke khazaanon ko Allah ki raah mein kharch kiya jaeyga."
7328,Yunus aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se Sufiyan ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki.
7329,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, unmein se (ye hadis bhi) hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Kisraa halaak ho gaya, phir uske baad Kisraa nahi hoga, aur qaisar bhi halaak ho jaeyga phir uske baad koi qaisar nahi hoga aur un donon ke khazaaney Allah ki raah mein taqseem kiye jaengey."
7330,"Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Kisraa halaak ho jaeyga to uske baad koi Kisraa nahi hoga. ( aagey ( unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ki manind (tarah) zikr kiya."
7331,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur abu-Kamil Jahdari ne kaha : hamein abu-Awana ne Samak-bin-Harab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : musalmanon ya ( farmaya : ( mominon ki aik jamat aale-Kisraa ke khazaaney ko , jo safaid (Imaarat) mein hai zaroor-zaroor fateh karegi. Quteba ne musalmanon ki (jamat) kaha aur kisi shak ka izhar nahi kiya."
7332,"Shoba ne Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir-bin-Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, ( aagey ( abu-Awana ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
7333,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Muhammad ne soor-bin-Zaid-daili se, unhon-ne abu-ghais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne aisey Shahar ke barey mein suna hai jiski aik taraf khushki mein hai aur dusri taraf samandar mein hai? unhon (sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne arz ki, ji haan , Allah ke rasool ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke iske khilaf banu-Ishaq mein se sattar (70) hazaar log jihad karengey, wahan pahunch kar wo utrein gey to hathiyaron se jang karengey na teer-andazi karengey, wo kahengey , ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' to us ( Shahar ( ki aik taraf gir jaeygi. Saur ne kaha : main hi janta hun ke unhon (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu)) ne wahi (kinara) kaha (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo samandar mein hai. phir wo dusri baar ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' kahengey to us ( Shahar (ka doosra kinaaraa bhi gir jaeyga. phir wo teesri baar ''لاالٰہ الا اللہ Allah ki qism اکبر'' kahengey to unke liye rasta khul jaeyga aur wo us ( Shahar ( mein dakhil ho jaeinge aur ghaneemat ka maal hasil karengey. jab wo maale-ghanimat taqseem kar rahe hongey to aik cheekhti hui awaz aaeygi jo kahegi : dajjal namudaar ho gaya. chunanche wo (musalman) har cheez chhod dengey aur wapas palat padein gey."
7334,Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne kaha : hamein soor-bin-Zaid daili ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7335,"Muhammad-bin-Bashir ne kaha : hamein Ubaidullah ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahood tum se jang karengey aur tum unhein achi tarah qatl karogey yahan tak ke patthar kahega : aey musalman ! ye Yahudi hai, aagey badh , usko qatl kar."
7336,Yahya ne hamein Ubaidullah se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur apni hadis mein kaha : ye Yahudi mere peechhey hai.
7337,"Umar-bin-Hamza ne kaha : maine Salim ko kehtey huey suna : hamein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum aur yahood aapas mein jang karogey, yahan tak ke patthar kahega : aey musalman ! ye mere peechhey aik Yahudi hai, aagey badh , usey qatl kar de."
7338,"ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Yahudi tum se jang karengey (aakhirkaar) tumhen un par tasallut ata kar diya jaeyga, yahan tak ke patthar (bhi) kahega : aey musalman ! ye Yahudi mere peechhey hai, usko qatl kar do."
7339,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke musalman yahudiyon ke khilaf jang ladein gey aur musalman unko qatl karengey. yahan tak ke Yahudi darakht ya patthar ke peechhey chhipey ga aur patthar ya darakht kahega : aey musalman ! aey Allah ke bandey ! mere peechhey ye aik Yahudi hai aagey badh , usko qatl kar de, siwaey gharqad ke darakht ke (wo nahi kahega) kyonke wo yahood ka darakht hai."
7340,"abul-Ahwas aur abu-Awana donon ne Samak se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir-bin-samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : qiyamat se pahley kai kazzaab (jhoote) hongey. abul-Ahwas ki hadis mein unhon ( abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ( ne mazeed kaha ke maine unse puchha : kya aap ne ye ( baat ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni? unhon-ne kaha : haan."
7341,"aur ibne-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne mujhey hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Samak se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki. Samak ne kaha : maine apne bhai ko kehtey huey suna ke Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : un ( jhooton ( se bach kar raho."
7342,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi, yahan tak ke dajjaalon aur kazzaabon (jhooton) ko bheja jaeyga jo tees ke qareeb hongey. unmein se har aik dawa karta hoga ke wo Allah ka rasool hai."
7343,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : yahan tak ke wo (shaitan ki taraf se) maboos bin kar (bhejey hue) aaeingey."
7344,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah ( ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke ham chand ladkon ke paas se guzrey, unmein ibne-Sayyaad-bhi tha, sab bachchey bhag gaey aur ibne-Sayyaad baith gaya, to aisa laga ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat ko na-pasand kiya hai. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : terey hath khaak aalud hon ! kya to gawahi deta hai ke main Allah ka rasool hon? usne kaha : nahi. balke kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka rasool hon? Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mujhey ijazat dijiye ki main isko qatl kar dun, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye wahi hai jo tumhara guman hai to tum isko qatl nahi kar sako gey."
7345,"abu-Muawiya ne hamein khabar di, kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chal rahe they ke ham ibne-Sayyaad ke paas se guzrey , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : maine tumharey liye (dil mein) aik baat chhipaai hai. usne kaha wo 'dukh' hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : door dafa' ho ja ! to apni haisiyat se kabhi nahi badh sakega. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mujhey ijazat dein to main iski gardan mar dun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey chhod do, agar ye wahi hai jiska tumhen khof hai to tum isko qatl nahi kar sako gey."
7346,"Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Madina ke aik rastey main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki us ( ibne-Sayyaad ( se mulaqat hui, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : kya to ye gawahi deta hai ke main Allah ka rasool hon? usne kaha : kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka rasool hon? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main Allah par, uske farishton par aur uski kitaabon par imaan laya hun, tujhey kya nazar aata hai? usne kaha : mujhey pani par aik takht nazar aata hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum samandar par iblees ka takht dekh rahe ho, tujhey aur kya nazar aata hai? usne kaha : main 2 sachchon aur aik jhootey ko ya do jhooton aur aik sachey ko deikhta hun. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (iska mamla khud) iske samney gad-madd kar diya gaya hai. isey chhod do."
7347,"Moatamir ke walid (Sulaiman) ne kaha : hamein abu-Nazara ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha ke Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ibne-Sayyaad se mulaqat hui aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) they aur ibne-Sayyaad (doosrey ( ladkon ke sath tha, phir Jurairi ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7348,"Dawud ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Makka ki taraf jatey huey (rastey mein) mera aur ibne-Sayyaad ka sath ho gaya. us ne mujh se kaha : main kuchh aisey logon se mila hun jo samajhtey hain ke main dajjal hun, kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey nahi suna tha : uske bachchey nahi hongey? kaha : maine kaha : kyon nahi ! (suna tha) usne kaha : mere bachchey huey hain. kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kehtey huey nahi suna tha : wo (dajjal) Madina mein dakhil hoga aur na Makka mein? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! usne kaha : main Madina ke andar paida hua aur ab Makka ki taraf ja raha hun. unhon-ne kaha : phir apni baat ke aakhir mein us ne mujh se kaha : dekhein ! Allah ki qism ! main us (dajjal) ki jaey-paidaaish , uske rehney ki jagah aur wo kahan hai sab janta hun. (is tarah) us ne (apni haisiyat ke barey mein) mujhey uljhaa diya."
7349,"Moatamir ke walid (Sulaiman) abu-Nazara se aur wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey hain, kaha : mujh se ibne-Sayyaad ne aik baat kahi to mujhey uske samney sharmindagi mehsus hui. (us ne kaha : ( is baat par main aur logon ko ma'zoor samajhta hun, magar aey ashaabe-Muhammad ! aap logon ka mere sath kya mamla hai? kya Allah ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya tha : dajjal Yahudi hoga aur main musalman ho chuka hun. kaha : wo laa-walad (be-aulad) hoga. jabke meri aulad hui hai aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : Allah ne Makka (mein daakhila) is par haram kar diya hai. aur main Haj kar chuka hun. (hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : wo (ibne-Sayyaad) musalsal aisi baatein karta raha jin se imkan tha ke uski baat mere dil mein baith jaati. kaha : phir wo kehney laga : Allah ki qism ! is waqt mein ye baat janta hun ke wo kahan hai main uske maan-baap ko bhi janta hun. kaha us se puchha gaya ke kya tumhen ye baat achchhi lagey gi ke tumhi wo (dajjal) aadmi ho? us ne kaha, agar mujh ko uski pesh kash! ki jaey to main usey na-pasand nahi karunga."
7350,"Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ke ham Haj ya Umra ko nikley aur hamarey sath ibne-Sayyaad bhi tha. aik manzil mein ham utrey , log idhar-udhar chaley gaey aur main aur ibne-Sayyaad donon reh gaey. mujhey is wjah se us se sakht wahshat hui ke log uske barey mein jo kaha kartey they (ke dajjal hai) ibne-Sayyaad apna asbaab lekar aaya aur mere asbaab ke sath rakh diya (mujhey aur zyada wahshat hui) maine kaha ke garmi bahut hai agar to apna asbaab us darakht ke nichey rakhey to behtar hai. us ne aisa hi kiya. phir hamein bakriyan dikhlai di. ibne-Sayyaad gaya aur doodh lekar aaya aur kehney laga ke abu-Saeed ! doodh pi. maine kaha ke garmi bahut hai aur doodh garm hai aur doodh na peeney ki iske siwa koi wjah na thi ke mujhey uske hath se peenaa bura malum hua. ibne-Sayyaad ne kaha ke aey abu-Saeed ! maine irada kiya hai ke aik rassi loon aur darakht mein latkaa kar apne aapko phaansi de loon un baton ki wjah se jo log mere haq mein kehtey hain. aey abu-Saeed ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis itni kis se posheeda hai jitni tum Ansar ke logon se posheeda hai. kya tum sab logon se zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis ko nahi jantey? kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne nahi farmaya ke dajjal kaafir hoga aur main to musalman hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya ke dajjal laa-walad hoga aur meri aulad Madina mein maujood hai. kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye nahi farmaya ke dajjal Madina mein aur Makka mein na jaeyga aur main Madina se aa raha hun aur Makka ko ja raha hoon? saiyedna abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke) uski aisi baton ki wjah se) qareeb tha ke main uska tarafdaar bin jaun (aur logon ka uske barey mein kehna ghalat samjhoon) ke phir kehney laga albatta Allah ki qism ! main dajjal ko pehchanta hun aur uske paidaaish ka maqam janta hun aur ye bhi janta hun ke ab wo kahan hai. kaha : maine us se kaha : baqi Sara din terey liye tabahi aur halaakat ho ! (tera us se itna qurb (nazdeeki) kaisey hua? ("
7351,"abu-Muslima ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Sayyaad se farmaya : jannat ki mitti kaisi hai? usne kaha : aey abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! baareek safaid , kastoori (jaisi) hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tu ney sach kaha."
7352,"Jurairi ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke ibne-Sayyaad ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jannat ki mitti ke mutaalliq sawal kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : baareek safaid , khalis kastoori (ki tarah) hai."
7353,"Muhammad-bin-Munkadir se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko dekha, wo Allah ki qism kha kar keh rahe they ke ibne-Sayyaad dajjal hai. maine kaha : aap (is baat par) Allah ki qism kha rahe hain? unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko is baat par qism khaatey huey dekha tha aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par inkar nahi farmaya tha."
7354,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne unhein bataya , unhein Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chand logon mein ibne-Sayyaad ke paas gaey yahan tak ke usey bani-maghaala ke qil'ey ke paas ladkon ke sath kheltey huey dekha un dinon ibne-Sayyaad jawaani ke qareeb tha. usko khabar na hui yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski peeth par apna hath maara. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke kya to is baat ki gawahi deta hai ke main Allah Taala ka rasool hun? ibne-Sayyaad ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf dekha aur kaha ke main gawahi deta hun ke tum ummiyeenn ke rasool ho (ummi kehtey hain un-padh aur be-taleem ko). phir ibne-Sayyaad ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ke tum is baat ki gawahi detey ho ke main Allah Taala ka rasool hun? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is baat ka kuchh jawab na diya? (aur us se musalman honey ki darkhaast na ki kyonke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske musalman honey se maayoos ho gaey aur aik riwayat mein saad mohmila se yani Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko laat se maara) aur farmaya ke main Allah par aur uske rasulon par imaan laya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha ke tujhey kya dikhai deta hai? wo bola ke mere paas kabhi sachcha aata hai aur kabhi jhoota. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tera kaam gad-bad ho gaya (yani mila-jula haq aur baatil donon se). phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tujh se poochhney ke liye aik baat dil mein chhipaai hai. ibne-Sayyaad ne kaha ke wo dukkha ( dhuaan ( hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke zaleel ho, to apni qadr se kahan badh sakta hai? saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! mujhey chhodiye mein iski gardan maarta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye wahi (yani dajjal) hai to to usko mar na sakega aur agar ye wo (dajjal) nahi hai to tujhey iska maarna behtar nahi hai."
7355,"Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain is (pichhle waqiey) ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Hazrat Ubai-ibne-Ka'b Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) khajooron ke us baagh mein gaey jis mein ibne-Sayyaad tha, baagh mein dakhil honey ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajooron ke tanon ki aad mein honey lagey taake us se pahley ke ibne-Sayyaad aapko dekhey aap uski koi baat sun lein, wo bistar par aik narm chadar main (usey odh kar leta) hua tha. uske andar se uski gungunaahat ki awaz aa rahi thi. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khajoor ke darakhton ki aad ley rahe they, to ibne-Sayyaad ki maan ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya aur wo ibne-Sayyaad se kehney lagi saaf !  aur ye ibne-Sayyaad ka naam tha. ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (aaey) hain. ibne-Sayyaad uchhal kar khada ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar wo usko (usi haalat mein) chhod deti to wo (apna mamla) waazeh kar deta."
7356,"Salim ne kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon main (khutba dene ke liye) khadey huey aur Allah Taala ki aisi tareef ki jiska wo ahal (haqdar) hai, phir aap ne dajjal ka zikr kiya aur farmaya : main tumhen us se khabardaar kar raha hun, aur har Nabi ne apni qaum ko us se khabardar kiya hai, be-shak Hazrat Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne bhi apni qaum ko us se khabardar kiya, lekin main tumhen iske mutaalliq aik aisi baat bataataa hun jo kisi Nabi ne apni qaum ko nahi batai. achchhi tarah jaan lo ke wo kaana hai aur Allah tabarak w taala kaana nahi hai. ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-Sabit Ansari ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aik sahabi se (riwaayat kartey huey) khabar di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jis roz logon ko dajjal ke barey mein khabar-daar kiya to farmaya : uski donon aankhon ke darmyan likha hua hai : kaafir har wo aadmi jo uske amal ko na-pasand karega usey padh lega ya (farmaya :) har momin usey padh lega aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke is baat ko achchhi tarah jaan lo ke tum mein se koi bhi marney tak apne rab ko hargiz nahi dekh sakega. (jabke dajjal ko sab log dekh rahe hongey.)"
7357,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saalim-bin-Abdullah ne bataya ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ki jamat ke sath jis mein Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, tashrif le gaey, yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ibne-Sayyaad ko dekha. wo us waqt bulooghat (jawani) ki umr ko pahunchne ke qareeb aik ladka tha. wo banu-Muawiya ke makaanon ke paas ladkon ke sath khel raha tha aur Umar-bin-Sabit ki hadis ke ikhtitaam tak Yunus ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur Yaqoob se riwayat ki hui hadis mein kaha : abi ( ibne-Kab (Raziallahu anhu)) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman : agar wo usey chhod deti to waazeh kar deta. ke barey mein kaha, agar uski maan usey chhod deti to apna mamla wo waazeh kar deta."
7358,"abd-bin-Humaid aur Salma-bin-shabeeb donon ne hamein Abdur-Razzaq se hadis bayan ki, ( unhon-ne kaha : ( hamein Mamar ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se chand logon ke sath , jin mein Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they, ibne-Sayyaad ke qareeb se guzrey. wo us waqt ladka tha aur banu-Maghaala ke makaanon ke qareeb ladkon ke sath khel raha tha. (aagey) jis tarah Yunus aur Saleh ki hadis hai magar abd-bin-Humaid ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Hazrat Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath khajooron ke baagh mein janey ka zikr nahi kiya."
7359,"Ayub ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik rastey mein ibne-Sayyaad se miley. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se koi aisi baat kahi jisne usey ghussa dila diya to wo itna phool gaya ke usne (poori) gali ko bhar diya, phir Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas gaey unko ye khabar mil chuki thi, unhon-ne unse farmaya, Allah Taala tum par raham farmaai ! tum ibne-Sayyaad se kya chahtey they? kya tumhen malum nahi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : dajjal ghussa aa jana ki wjah se hi (apni haqiqi sura mein) baraamad hoga."
7360,"Ibne-Aun ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Naafe kaha kartey they ke ibne-Sayyaad. (uskey barey mein) Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main us se do baar mila hun. aik baar mila to maine logon se kaha ke tum kehtey they ke ibne-Sayyaad dajjal hai? unhon-ne kaha ke nahi Allah ki qasam. maine kaha ke Allah ki qism ! tum ne mujhey jhoota kiya. tum mein se kuchh logon ne mujh se bayan kiya ke wo nahi marey ga, yahan tak ke tum sab mein zyada maaldaar aur sahibe-aulad hoga, to wo aaj ke din aisa hi hai. wo kehtey hain phir ibne-Sayyaad ne ham se baatein kin. phir main ibne-Sayyaad se juda hua. kehtey hain ke jab dobara mila to uski aankh phooli hui thi. maine kaha ke ye teri aankh Kab se aisey hai jo main dekh raha hoon? wo bola ke mujhey malum nahi. maine kaha ke aankh terey sar mein hai aur tujhey malum nahi ? wo bola ke agar Allah chahey to teri us lakdi mein aankh paida kar de. phir aisi awaz nikaali jaisey gadhaa zor se karta hai. unhon-ne kaha : mere sathiyon mein se aik samajhta hai ke mere paas jo dandaa tha maine usey iske sath itna maara ke wo dandaa toot gaya lekin main, Allah ki qism ! mujhey kuchh pata na chala . Naafe ne kaha ke saiyedna Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu), Ummul-Momenin (Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) (ke paas gaey aur unse ye haal bayan kiya to unhon-ne kaha ke ibne-Sayyaad se tera kya kaam tha? kya to nahi janta ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke awwal cheez jo dajjal ko logon par bhejey gi, wo uska ghussa hai."
7361,"Ubaidullah ne hamein Naafe se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ke samney dajjal ka zikr kiya to aap ne farmaya : Allah tabarak w taala kaana nahi hai sun rakho ! bila shubah Masih-dajjal dahini aankh se kaana hai. uski aankh is tarah hai jaisey ubhraa hua angoor ka daana."
7362,Ayub aur Musa-bin-Aqba donon ne Naafe se unhon-ne ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7363,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi Nabi nahi (guzra) magar us ne apni ummat ko kaaney kazzaab (jhutey) se daraayaa hai. yad rakho, wo kanaa hai jabke tumhara izzat aur jalaal wala rab kaana nahi us (dajjal) ki donon aankhon ke darmyan kafir likha hua hai."
7364,"Hisham ne Qatada se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal ki donon aankhon ke darmyan ک  ر yani kaafir likha hua hoga."
7365,Shuaib-bin-habhaab ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal be noor aankh wala hai aur uski donon aankhon ke darmyan likha hua hai kaafir. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uske hijjey kiye 'ک  ر '. usko har musalman padh lega.
7366,"Shaqiq ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal ki baain aankh (bhi) aib daar hogi aur baal ghaney guchchhey daar hongey uske sath aik jannat hogi aur aik dozakh hogi. uski dozakh (haqeeqat mein) jannat hogi aur uski jannat asl mein dozakh hogi."
7367,"abu-Malik Ashjai ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo kuch dajjal ke sath hoga usey main khud uski nisbat bhi zyada achchhi tarah janta hun. uske sath do chaltey huey dariya hongey. donon mein se aik bazahir safaid rang ka pani hoga aur doosra bazahir bhadakti hui aag hogi. agar koi shakhs usko paaley to us dariya ki taraf aaey jisey wo aag (ki tarah) dekh raha hai aur apni aankh band kare. phir apna sar jhukaaye aur is mein se piye to wo thanda pani hoga aur dajjal be-noor aankh wala hai uske uper mota naakhoona ( gosht ka tukda jo aankh mein paida ho jata hai) hoga. uski donon aankhon ke darmyan likha hoga kaafir. usey har momin likhney ( padhney ( wala ho ya na likhney ( padhney ( wala padh lega."
7368,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Shoba ne abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dajjal ke barey mein, (farmaya) be-shak uske sath  pani hoga aur aag hogi uski aag (asl mein) thanda pani hoga aur uska pani aag hogi to tum log (dhokey mein) halaak na ho jana."
7369,Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi.
7370,"Shuaib-bin-safwaan ne hamein abdul-Malik-bin-Umair se unhon-ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se unhon-ne Aqba-bin-Amr-abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, (Rabai ne) kaha : main un ( Aqba-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu)) ke sath Hazrat Huzaifa-bin-yamaan (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaya Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha : aap ne dajjal ke mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo hadis suni hai wo mujhey bayan kariye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal nikley gaa us ke sath pani hoga aur aag hogi. jo logon ko pani nazar aa raha hoga (wo) aag hogi aur jo logon ko aag nazar aa rahi hogi. wo thanda meethaa pani hoga tum mein se jo shakhs usko paaey wo usmein kood jaey jo usey aag nazar aa rahi ho. bila shubah wo meethaa pakeeza pani hoga. Hazrat Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ki tasdeeq kartey huey kaha, aur maine (bhi) ye hadis suni thi."
7371,"Nuaim-bin-abi-Hind ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se riwayat ki kaha : (eik baar jab) Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : dajjal ke sath jo kuchh hoga uska mujhey khud uski nisbat zyada ilm hai uske sath aik dariya pani ka hoga aur aik dariya aag ka hoga. jo tumhen nazar aayega ke wo aag hai, wo pani hoga aur jo tumhen nazar aayega ke wo pani hai, wo aag hogi. tum mein se jo shakhs usko paaey aur pani peenaa chahey wo us dariya se piye jo usey nazar aata hai ke wo aag hai. bila shubah wo usey pani paaeyga . Hazrat abu Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko isi tarah farmatey huey suna tha."
7372,"abu-Salma se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tumhen dajjal ke mutaalliq aisi baat na bataaun jo kisi Nabi ne apni ummat ko nahi batai. wo yaqeeni taur par kaana hoga. uske sath jannat aur jahannam ki tarah (do jaghein samney) aaein gi. jiske barey mein wo kahey ke jannat hai wo (asl mein) jahannam hogi. maine isi tarah tumhen us se khabardar kar diya hai. jis tarah Hazrat Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne uske barey main apni qaum ko khabardaar kiya tha."
7373,"abu khaisma Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Muhammad-bin-Mehran razi ne mujhey hadis bayan ki. alfaz razi ke hain. kaha : hamein Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed-bin-Jaabir ne Yahya-bin-Jaabir qaazi teiswin se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Jubair-bin-Nufair se. unhon-ne apne walid Jubair-bin-Nufair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat nawaas-bin-samaan (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik subah dajjal ka zikr kiya. aap ne us (ke zikr ke dauran) mein kabhi awaz dheemi ki kabhi unchi ki. yahan tak ke hamein aisey laga jaisey wo khajooron ke jhund mein maujood hai. jab Sham ko ham aap ke paas (dobara) aaey to aap ne ham mein us (shadeed tassur) ko bhaanp liya. aap ne ham se puchha tum logon ko kya hua hai? ham ne kaha Allah ke rasool ! subah ke waqt aap ne dajjal ka zikr farmaya to aap ki awaz mein (aisa) utaar-chadhaao tha ke ham ne samjha ke wo khajooron ke jhund mein maujood hai. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya : mujhey tum logon (haazirin) par dajjal ke alawa doosrey (jahannam ki taraf bulaney walon) ka zyada khof hai agar wo nikalta hai aur main tumharey darmyan maujood hun to tumhari taraf se uske khilaf (uske inkar ke liye) dalaayel dene wala main hunga aur agar wo nikla aur main maujood na hua to har aadmi apni taraf se hujjat qaaim karne wala khud hoga aur Allah har musalman par mera khaleefa (khud nigahbaan) hoga. wo guchchhey daar baalon wala aik jawan shakhs hai uski aik aankh be-noor hai. main aik tarah se usko abdul-azeez-bin-qatan se tashbeeh deta hun. tum mein se jo usey paaey to uske samney sura kahaf ki shuruati aayatein padhey. wo Iraq aur Sham (Syria) ke darmyan aik rastey se nikal kar aayega. wo daain taraf bhi tabahi machaaney wala hoga aur baain taraf bhi. aey Allah ke bando ! tum Sabit qadam rehna. ham ne arz kiya Allah ke rasool ! zamin mein uski tezi ki raftaar kya hogi ? aap ne farmaya : badal ki tarah jiske peechhey hawa ho. wo aik qaum ke paas aayega unhein dawat dega wo is par imaan laaengey aur uski baatein maanein gey. to wo aasman (ke badal) ko hukm dega. wo barish barsaey ga aur wo zamin ko hukm dega to wo faslein ugaaey gi. Sham ke oqaat mein unke janwar ( charaagaahon se) wapas aaeingey to unke kohan sabse zyada oonchey aur than intihai zyada bharey huey aur kokhein phaili hui hongi. phir aik (aur) qaum ke paas aayega aur unhein (bhi) dawat dega. wo uski baat thukraa dengey. wo unhein chhod kar chala jaeyga to wo qahat ka shikar ho jaengey. unke maal maweshi mein se koi cheez unke hath mein nahi hogi. wo (dajjal) banjar zamin mein se guzrey ga to us se kahega apne khazaaney nikal to us (banjar zameen) ke khazaaney is tarah (nikal kar) uske peechhey lag jaengey jis tarah shehad ki makkhiyon ki raaniyaan hain. phir wo aik bhar-poor jawan ko bulaeyga aur usey talwaar mar kar (yakbaargi) do hisson mein taqseem kar dega jaisey nishana banaya janey wala hadaf (yakdam tukdey ho gaya) ho. phir wo usey bulaeyga to wo (zinda hokar) dekhtey huey chehrey ke sath hanstaa hua aayega. wo (dajjal) usi aalim mein hoga jab Allah Taala Masih-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ko maabood farma dega. wo dimashq ke hissey mein aik safaid meenaar ke qareeb do kesri kapdon mein do farishton ke kandhon par hath rakhey huey utrein gey. jab wo apna sar jhukaay gey to qatrey girein gey aur sar uthayen gey to us se chamaktey motiyon ki tarah pani ki boondein girein gi. kisi kaafir ke liye jo aap ki saans ki khushbu paaeyga marney ke siwa koi chaara nahi hoga. unki saans (ki khushbu) wahan tak pahuncheygi jahan tak unki nazar jaeygi. aap (Alaihissalam) usey dhoondein gey to usey lud ( LUDIYA (ke darwazey par paeingey aur usey qatl kar dengey. phir Esa-bin-Maryam (Alaihissalam) ke paas wo log aaeingey jinhein Allah ne us ( dajjal ke daam mein aaney) se mehfooz rakha hoga to wo apne hath unke chehron par pherein gey aur unhein jannat mein unke darjaat ki khabar dengey. wo usi aalim mein hongey ke Allah Taala Esa (Alaihissalam) ki taraf wahi farmaeyga maine apne (paida kiye huey) bandon ko bahar nikal diya hai unse jang karne ki taqat kisi mein nahi. aap meri bandagi karne walon ko ikattha karke taur ki taraf ley jayen aur Allah yaajooj maajooj ko bhej dega. wo har unchi jagah se umadtey huey aaeingey. unke pahley log (meethey pani ki bahut badi jheel) buhaira tabriya se guzrengey aur is mein jo (pani) hoga usey pee jaeinge phir aakhiri log guzrengey to kahengey. kabhi is (buhaira) mein (bhi) pani hoga. Allah ke Nabi Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi mahsoor ho kar reh jaengey. yahan tak ke unmein se kisi aik ke liye bail ka sar us se behtar (qeemti) hoga jitney aaj tumharey liye so Dinar hain. Allah ke Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi gid-gidaa kar duaein karengey to Allah Taala un (yaajooj maajooj) par unki gardanon mein keedon ka azab nazil kar dega to wo aik insan ke marney ki tarah (yakbaargi) iska shikar ho jaengey. phir Allah ke Nabi Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi utar kar (maidaani) zamin par aaeingey to unhein zamin mein baalisht bhar bhi jagah nahi milegi. jawan ki gandagi aur badboo se bhari hui na ho. is par hazarat Esa (Alaihissalam) aur unke sathi Allah ke samney gid-gidaaein gey to Allah Taala bakhti oonton ke jaisi lambi gardanon ki tarah (ki gardanon waale) parindey bhejeyga jo unhein uthayen gey aur jahan Allah chaahega ja phenkei gey. phir Allah Taala aisi barish bhejeyga jis se koi ghar enton ka ho ya oon ka (khema) oat muhaiya nahi kar sakega. wo zamin ko dho kar sheeshey ki tarah (saaf) kar chhodegi. phir zamin se kaha jaeyga apne phal ugaao aur apni barkat lota lao to us waqt aik anaar ko poori jamat khaaey gi aur uske chhilkey se saaya hasil karegi aur doodh mein (itni) barkat dali jaeygi ke oontni ka aik baar ka doodh logon ki aik badi jamat ko kafi hoga aur gaaey ka aik baar ka doodh logon ke qabeeley ko kafi hoga aur bakri ka aik baar ka doodh qabeeley ki aik shaakh ko kafi hoga. wo usi aalim mein reh rahe hongey. ke Allah Taala aik umda hawa bhejeyga wo logon ko unki baghlon ke nichey se pakdey gi aur har momin aur har musalman ki Rooh qabz kar leygi aur bad tareen log baqi reh jaeinge wo gadhon ki tarah (bar-sare-aam) aapas mein ikhtilat (milap) karengey to unhi par qiyamat qaaim hogi."
7374,Ali-bin-Hujr Sadi ne hamein hadis bayan ki kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed-bin-Jaabir aur Waleed-bin-Muslim ne hadis bayan ki (Ali) ibne-hijr ne kaha : aik ki hadis doosrey ki hadis mein shamil ho gaee hai. unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Yazeed-bin-Jaabir se usi ki sanad ke sath jis tarah ham ne zikr kiya usi ke mutabiq bayan kiya aur us jumley ke baad usmein kabhi pani tha mazeed bayan kiya phir wo (aagey) chalein gey yahan tak ke wo Jabal khumr tak pahunchein gey aur wo baitul-maqdis ka pahaad hai to kahengey jo koi bhi zamin mein tha ham ne usey qatl kar diya aao ! ab usey qatl karein jo aasman mein hai phir wo apne teeron (jaisey hathiyaaron) ko aasman ki taraf chalaaein gey. to Allah Taala unke hathiyaaron ko khoon aalud karke unhi ki taraf wapas bhej dega aur ibne-hijr ki riwayat mein hai maine apne (paida kiye huey) bandon ko utara hai kisi aik ke paas bhi unse jang karne ki taqat nahi.
7375,Saleh ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki kaha : mujhey Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey sath dajjal ke barey mein lambi guftgu farmai. usmein aap ne hamarey samney jo bayan kiya usmein (ye bhi) tha ke aap ne farmaya : wo aayega is par Madina ke rastey haram kar diye gaey hongey. wo Madina se muttasil (lagi hui) aik narm shoreeli zamin tak pahunchega uske paas aik aadmi (Madina se) nikal kar jaeyga jo logon mein se behtreen ya behtreen logon mein se aik hoga aur us se kahega. main gawahi deta hun ke to wahi dajjal hai jiske barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni guftgu mein hamein bataya tha. to dajjal (apne sath maujood logon se) kahey) ga tum logon ka kya khayal hai ke agar main is shakhs ko qatl kar dun aur phir usey zinda kar dun to kya is mamley main tumhen koi shak (baqi) rahega? wo kahengey nahi. wo us shakhs ko qatl karega aur dobara zinda kar dega. jab wo us shakhs ko zinda karega to wo us se kahega . Allah ki qism ! tumharey barey mein mujhey ab se pahley is se zyada baseerat (sujh-bujh) kabhi hasil nahi thi. farmaya : dajjal usey qatl karna chaahega lekin usey us shakhs par tasallut hasil nahi ho sakega.
7376,Shuaib ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
7377,"abu wddaak ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : dajjal niklega to mominon mein se aik shakhs uska rukh karey gaa usey aslaha bardaar muhaafiz yani dajjal ke aslaha bardaar muhaafiz milein gey aur us se poochhein gey. kahan jana chahtey ho? wo kahega . main us shakhs ki taraf jana chahta hun jo (ab) namudaar hua hai wo us se kahengey. kya tum hamarey rab par imaan nahi rakhtey? wo kahega, hamarey rab (ki ruboobiyat (khudaai) aur sifaat (khubiyon)) mein koi posheedgi nahi wo (uski baat par mutmain na hotey huey) kahengey. isko qatl kar do. phir wo aik doosrey se kahengey. kya hamarey rab ne hamein mana nahi kiya tha ke us (ke samney pesh karne) se pahley kisi ko qatl na karo. wo usey dajjal ke paas ley jaengey. wo momin jab usey dekhega to kahega logo ! ye wahi dajjal hai jiska zikr Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha. farmaya : to dajjal iske barey mein hukm dega to us (ke aaza ( ko kheench kar baandh diya jaeyga phir wo kahega. usey pakdo aur iska sar aur munh tod do. to (mar-mar kar) iska pet aur iski kamar choodi kar di jaeygi. farmaya : phir wo (dajjal) kahega . kya tum mujh par imaan nahi laaogey? farmaya : to wo kahega tum jhootey (bnaawati) Masih ho. farmaya : phir iske barey mein hukm diya jaeyga to uski peshani se usey aari ke sath chira jaeyga yahan tak ke iske donon paon alag alag kar diye jaengey. farmaya : phir dajjal donon tukdon ke darmyan chalega . phir us se kahega. khadey ho jao chunanche wo seedha khada ho jaeyga farmaya : wo phir us se kahega kya mujh par imaan latey ho? wo kahega . (is sab kuchh se) tumharey barey mein meri baseerat mein izaafey ke siwa aur kuchh nahi hua. farmaya : phir wo shakhs kahega logo ! ye (dajjal) ab mere baad logon mein kisi ke sath aisa nahi kar sakega. farmaya : dajjal usey zabah karne ke liye pakdega to uski gardan se uski hansli ki haddiyon tak (ka hissa) taanbey ka banaya jaeyga wo kisi tareeqey se (usey zabah) na kar sakega. farmaya, to wo iske donon paon aur donon hathon se pakad kar usey phainkey ga . log samjhein gey us (dajjal) ne isey aag mein phenk diya hai jabke (asl mein wo) jannat mein daal diya jaeyga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : shahadat mein rabbul-aalameen ke samney ye shakhs sab logon se bada hai."
7378,"Ibrahim-bin-Humaid Ruwasi ne Ismail-bin-abi-Khalid se unhon-ne Qais-bin-abi-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se dajjal ke barey mein jitna maine puchha us se zyada kisi ne nahi poochha. aap ne farmaya is (ke hawale) se tumhen kya baat itna thakaa rahi hai? wo tumhen nuqsan nahi pahunchaeyga. kaha : maine arz ki, Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! log kehtey hain uske sath khaney (ke dher) aur (pani ke) dariya hongey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ke nazdeek wo us se haqeer tar hai. (ke aisi chizon ke zariey se musalmanon ko gumrah kar sakey.)"
7379,"Hushaim ne Ismail se unhon-ne Qais se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se dajjal ke barey mein jitna maine puchha us se zyada kisi ne nahi poochha, aap ne farmaya : tumharey sawal ka (sabab) kya hai? kaha : maine kaha wo (log) kehtey hain uske sath roti aur gosht ke pahaad aur pani ka dariyaa hoga farmaya : wo Allah ke nazdeek is se zyada haqeer (tuchh) hai."
7380,"Wakee , Jareer, Sufiyan , Yazid-bin-Harun aur abu-Usama sab ne Ismail se isi sanad ke sath Ibrahim-bin-Humaid ki tarah riwayat ki aur Yazeed ki hadis mein mazeed ye hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : mere betey !"
7381,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Nauman-bin-Saalim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Yaqoob-bin-Aasim-bin-Urwa-bin-Masood Saqafi se suna, wo kehtey hain maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unke paas aik shakhs aaya aur kaha : ye kya hadis hai jo aap bayan kartey hain. ke falan-falan baat honey tak qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi unhon-ne Subhan-Allah ! ya 'لاالہ الااللہ' ya us jaisa koi kalima kaha : (aur kehney lagey ( maine pukhta irada kar liya ke main kisi ko kabhi koi baat bayan nahi karunga . maine ye kaha tha tum log thodey waqt baad bahut bada mamla dekhogey. Baitullah ko jalaa diya jaeyga aur ye hoga aur ye hoga. phir kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein dajjal namudaar hoga aur chalis (40) mujhey yad nahi ke chalis (40) din (farmaey) ya chalis (40) mahiney ya chalis (40) saal rahega to Allah Taala Hazrat Esa (Alaihissalam) ko bhej dengey. wo is tarah hain jaisey Hazrat Urwa-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aap usey dhoondein gey aur usey halaak kar dengey. phir log saat (7) saal tak is haalat mein raheingey. ke koi se do aadmiyon ke darmyan dushmani tak na hogi phir Allah Taala Sham (Syria) ki taraf se aik thandi hawa chalaaey ga to poori zamin par aik bhi aisa aadmi nahi rahega jiske dil mein zarra barabar bhalai ya imaan hoga. magar wo hawa uski Rooh qabz karegi yahan tak kaha agar tum mein se koi shakhs pahaad ke jigar mein ghus jaeyga to wahan bhi wo (hawa) dakhil ho jaeygi. yahan tak ke uski Rooh qabz kar leygi. unhon-ne kaha : ye baat maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni. aap ne farmaya : parindon jaisa halkaapan aur darindon jaisi aqlein rakhney waley bad tareen log baqi reh jaengey. na achchhai ko achchha samjhein gey na burai ko bura jaanein gey. shaitan koi shakl ikhtiyar karke unke paas aayega aur kahega : kya tum meri baat par amal nahi karogey? wo kahengey to hamein kya hukm deta hai? wo unhein but poojney ka hukm dega wo usi haalat mein raheingey unka rizq utartaa hoga unki ma'eeshat (arthviyavastha) bahut achi hogi. phir Saur phoonkaa jaeyga jo bhi usey suney ga wo gardan ki aik taraf ko jhukaaey ga aur dusri taraf ko uncha karega (gardanein tedhi ho jaeyngi) sabse pahlaa shakhs jo usey suney gaa wo apne oonton ke hauz ki lipaai kar raha hoga. wo pachhaad kha kar gir jaeyga aur doosrey log bhi gir (kar mar) jaengey. iske baad Allah Taala aik barish nazil farmaeyga . jo aik phuwaar ki tarah hogi. ya saaey ki tarah hogi. shak karne waley Nauman (bin-Saalim) hain us se insanon ke jism ug aaeingey. phir Saur mein dusri baar phoonk maari jaeygi. to wo sab log khadey huey dekh rahe hongey, ( zinda ho jaeinge ( phir kaha jaeyga logo ! apne parwardigar ki taraf aao ! aur (farishton se kaha jaeyga :) unko la khada karo unse sawal poochhey jaengey. hukm diya jaeyga aag mein bhejey janey walon ko (apni safon se) bahar nikaalo , puchha jaeyga kitnon mein se (kitney?) kaha jaeyga har hazaar mein se na-sau-ninyaanwe (999). unhon-ne kaha : to ye wo din hoga jo bachchon ko boodha kar dega aur wahi din hoga jab pindli se parda hata (kar deedaar jamaal karaya) jaeyga."
7382,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Nauman-bin-Saalim se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Yaqoob-bin-Aasim-bin-Urwa-bin-Masood se suna, unhon-ne kaha : maine aik shakhs ko suna, us ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : aap ye kehtey hain ke falan-falan (baat poori ho janey) par qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine ye irada kar liya hai ke main tum logon ko koi hadis na sunaun. maine to ye kaha tha ke tum thodi muddat ke baad aik bada mamla dekhogey to Baitullah ke jalney ka waqia ho gaya. Shoba ne ye alfaz kahey ya us se miltey-jultey alfaz kahey. Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat mein dajjal namudaar hoga aur (uske baad Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne) Muaz ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur apni hadis mein kaha : koi aik shakhs bhi jiske dil mein zarra barabar imaan ho, nahi bachey ga magar wo (hoga) uski Rooh qabz kar leygi Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : Shoba ne mujhey ye hadis kai baar sunai aur maine (kai baar) usey unke samney dohraya."
7383,"Muhammad-bin-Bashir ne abu-Hayyan se, unhon-ne abu-Zura se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aisi hadis suni hai jis ko sunney ke baad main usey bhula nahi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : namudaar honey wali sabse pahley nishani maghrib se suraj ka tuloo hona aur din chadhey logon ke samney zamin ke chaupaaey ka nikalnaa hai. unmein se jo bhi nishani dusri se pahley zahir hogi, dusri uske baad jald namudaar ho jaeygi."
7384,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein abu-Hayyan ne Abu-Zaraa se bayan kiya, kaha : musalmanon mein se teen shakhs Madina mein Marwaan-bin-Hakam ke paas baithey they aur usey qiyamat ki nishaniyan bayan kartey huey sun rahe they ke unmein se pehli dajjal ka zuhoor hoga, is par Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (tum log yun samjho ke) Marwan ne kuchh bhi nahi kaha (kyonke uski baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farman ke mutabiq nahi) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik hadis suni thi jisey main bhula nahi. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. phir usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kiya."
7385,"Sufiyan ne abu-Hayyan se aur unhon-ne abu-Zura se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : logon ne mardaan ki maujoodgi mein qiyamat ke barey mein muzaakra kiya to Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. ( aagey ( un donon ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya aur din chadhney ke waqt ka zikar nahi kiya."
7386,"ibne-bareeda ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sharaheel-Shabi ne jinka talluq shaabu-hamdaan se tha, hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Suhak-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ki behen saiyeda Fatima-binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se sawal kiya, wo awwaleen hijrat karne walon mein se thin ke aap mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aisi hadis bayan karein jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (bilaa-waasta) suni ho. wo bolin ke achchha , agar tum ye chahtey ho to , main bayan karun gi. unhon-ne kaha ke haan, bayan karo. Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke maine ibne-Mugheera (Raziallahu anhu) se nikah kiya aur wo un dinon Quraish ke umda jawaanon mein se they, phir wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath pahley hi jihad mein Shahid ho gaey. jab main bewa ho gaee to mujhey Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se chand ke sath aa kar nikah ka paigham diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne Maula Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) ke liye paigham bheja aur main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ye hadis sun chuki thi ke jo shakhs mujh se mohabbat rakhey, usko chahiye ke Usama (Raziallahu anhu) se bhi mohabbat rakhey. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se is barey mein guftgu ki to maine kaha ke mere kaam ka ikhtiyar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis se chaahein nikah kar dijiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar chali jao aur umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) Ansar mein aik maaldaar aurat thi aur Allah ki raah mein bahut zyada kharch karti thin, uske paas mehman utartey they. maine arz kiya ke bahut achchha, main umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chali jaaungi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas mat ja uske paas mehman bahut aatey hain aur mujhey bura malum hota hai ke kahin teri odhni gir jaey ya teri pindliyon par se kapda hat jaey aur log terey badan mein se wo dekhein jo tujhey bura lagey ga. tum apne chacha ke betey Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas chali jao aur wo bani-fahar mein se aik shakhs tha aur fahar Quraish ki aik shaakh hai aur wo us qabeele mein se tha jis mein se Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) bhi thin. phir Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke main unke ghar mein chali gaee. jab meri iddat guzar gaee to maine pukarney waley ki awaz suni aur wo pukarney wala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka manaadi tha, wo pukar raha tha ke Namaz ke liye jama ho jao. main bhi masjid ki taraf nikli aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi. main us saf mein thi jis mein auratein logon ke peechhey thin. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padh li to member par baithey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hans rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har aik aadmi apni Namaz ki jagah par rahe. phir farmaya ke tum jantey ho ke maine tumhen kyon ikattha kiya hai? sahaba boley ke Allah aur uska rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khub jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki qism maine tumhen raghbat (dilchaspi) dilaane ya daraane ke liye jama nahi kiya, balke isliye jama kiya ke Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) aik nasrani tha, wo aaya aur us ne bait ki aur musalman hua aur mujh se aik hadis bayan ki jo us hadis ke muwafiq hai jo main tum se dajjal ke barey mein bayan kiya karta tha. us ne bayan kiya ke wo yani Tameem samandar ke jahaz mein tees aadmiyon ke sath sawar hua jo lakhm aur juzaam ki qaum mein se they, to unse aik mahina bhar samandar ki lahrein khelti rahin. phir wo log samandar mein doobtey suraj ki taraf aik jazeerey ke kinarey ja lagey. to wo jahaz se pulwar (yani chhoti kashti) mein baithey aur jazeerey mein dakhil ho gaey wahan unko aik janwar mila jo ke bhari dam , bahut baalon wala ke iska aglaa pichhlaa hissey baalon ke hujoom se malum na hota tha. logon ne us se kaha ke aey kambakht to kya cheez hai? usne kaha ke main jaasus hun. logon ne kaha ke jaasus kya? usne kaha ke us mard ke paas chalo jo dair (rahibon ki imaarat) mein hai, ke wo tumhari khabar ka bahut mushtaaq (khahishmand) hai. Tameem (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab us ne mard ka naam liya to ham us janwar se darey ke kahin shaitan na ho. Tameem (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke phir ham daudtey huey (yani jaldi) 'dair' mein dakhil huey. dekha to wahan aik badey qad ka aadmi hai ke ham ne itna bada aadmi aur waisaa sakht jakdaa hua kabhi nahi dekha. uske donon hath gardan ke sath bandhey huey they aur donon raanon se takhnon tak lohey se jakdaa hua tha. ham ne kaha ke aey kambakht ! to kya cheez hai? usne kaha tum meri khabar par qaabu pa gaey ho (yani mera haal to tum ko ab malum ho jaaeyga), tum apna haal bataao ke tum kon ho? logon ne kaha ke ham Arab log hain, samandar mein jahaz mein sawar huey they, lekin jab ham sawar huey to samandar ko josh mein paya phir aik mahiney ki muddat tak lahar ham se khelti rahi , phir ham is jazeerey mein aa lagey to chhoti kashti mein baith kar jazeerey mein dakhil huey, to hamein aik bhari dam ka aur bahut baalon wala janwar mila, ham uske baalon ki kasarat ki wjah se uska aglaa pichhlaa hissey na pehchantey they. ham ne us se kaha ke aey kambakht ! to kya cheez hai? usne kaha ke main jaasus hun. ham ne kaha ke jaasus kya? usne kaha ke us mard ke paas chalo jo 'dair' mein hai aur wo tumhari khabar ka bahut mushtaaq hai. to ham teri taraf daudtey huey aaey aur ham us se darey ke kahin bhoot-paret na ho. phir us mard ne kaha ke mujhey baisaan ke nakhlistaan (khajuron) ki khabar do. ham ne kaha ke to uska kon sa haal poochhta hai? usne kaha ke main uske nakhlistaan (khajur ke paidon) ke barey mein poochhta hun ke wo phal detey hai? ham ne us se kaha ke haan, phal detey hai. usne kaha ke khabardaar raho an-qareeb wo na phaley gein. usne kaha ke mujhey tabriya ke dariya ke barey mein batlao . ham ne kaha ke to us dariya ka kon sa haal poochhta hai? wo bola ke usmein pani hai? logon ne kaha ke usmein bahut pani hai. usne kaha ke albatta uska pani an-qareeb khatm ho jaeyga phir usne kaha ke mujhey zughar ke chashmey ke barey mein khabar do. logon ne kaha ke uska kya haal poochhta hai? usne kaha ke us chashmey mein pani hai aur wahan ke log us pani se kheti kartey hain? ham ne us se kaha ke haan ! usmein bahut pani hai aur wahan ke log uske pani se kheti kartey hain. usne kaha ke mujhey ummiyon ke paighambar ke barey mein khabar do unhonne kya kiya? logon ne kaha ke wo Makka se nikley hain aur Madina mein gaey hain. usne kaha ke kya Arab ke log unse ladey? ham ne kaha ke haan. usne kaha ke unhon-ne Arbon ke sath kya kiya ? ham ne kaha ke wo apne gird aur pesh ke Arbon par ghalib huey aur unhon-ne unki itaat ki. usne kaha ke ye baat ho chuki? ham ne kaha ke haan. usne kaha ke khabardaar raho ye baat unke haq mein behtar hai ke paighambar ke perokar hon aur albatta main tum se apna haal kehta hun ke main Masih (dajjal) hun aur albatta wo zamana qareeb hai ke jab mujhey nikalney ki ijazat hogi. isliye main niklun ga aur sair karunga aur kisi basti ko na chhodunga jahan chalis (40) raat ke andar na jaun, siwaey Makka aur taiba ke , ke wahan jana mujh par haram hai yani mana hai. jab main un donon bastiyon mein se kisi ke andar jana chaahoon ga to mere aagey aik farishta badh aayega aur uske hath mein nangi talwaar hogi, wo mujhey wahan janey se rok dega aur albatta uske har aik naakey par Farishtey hongey jo uski chaukidaari karengey. Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni chhadi member par mar kar farmaya ke taiba yahi hai, taiba yahi hai, taiba yahi hai. yani taiba se murad Madina Munawra hai. khabardaar raho ! bhala main tum ko is haal ki khabar de nahi chuka hun? to ashaab ne kaha ke haan. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey Tameem (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat achi lagi jo us cheez ke muwafiq hui jo maine tum logon se dajjal aur Madina aur Makka ke haal se farma diya tha. khabardaar ho ke wo Sham (Syria) ya Yaman ke samandar mein hai? nahi balke wo mashriq ki taraf hai, wo mashriq ki taraf hai, wo mashriq ki taraf hai (mashriq ki taraf bahare-Hind hai shayad dajjal bahare-Hind ke kisi jazeera mein ho (aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mashriq ki taraf ishara kya. Sayeda Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ye hadis maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yad rakhi hai."
7387,"sayyaar-abul-hakam ne kaha : hamein Shabi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, unhon-ne hamein taaza khajooron ka tohfa diya jinko ibne-taab ki taaza khajoorein kaha jata tha aur jau ke sattu pilaaey, maine unse us aurat ke barey mein puchha jis ko teen talaaqein di gaee hon ke wo iddat kahan guzaarey gi? unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere shauhar ne teen talaaqein di thin to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey ijazat di thi ke main apne ghar walon ke darmyan iddat guzaar loon, (hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : phir (iddat ke baad) logon mein ye elaan kiya gaya ke Namaz ki jamat honey wali hai, main bhi doosrey logon ke sath Namaz ke liye chal di, mein aurton ki pehli saf mein thi jo mardon ki aakhiri saf ke peechhey thi. unhon-ne kaha : maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par khutba de rahe they, aap ne farmaya : Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) ke chacha ke betey (unke qabeeley se talluq rakhney waley rishtedar ( samandar (ke jahaz) mein sawar huey. uskey baad (sayyaar ne poori) hadis bayan ki aur is mein mazeed kaha ke (hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne) kaha : aisey lagta hai ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh rahi hun, aap ne apne asaa ko zamin ki taraf jhukaya aur farmaya : ye taiba hai. aap ki murad Madina se thi."
7388,"ghailaan-bin-Jareer ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas Hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya ke wo samandar (ke jahaz) mein sawar huey to unka jahaz rastey se hat gaya, wo aik jazeerey mein ja utrey, wo us jazeerey mein nikal kar pani dhoondney lagey, wahan aik insan se mulaqat hui jo apne baal ghaseet raha tha, phir (poori) hadis bayan ki aur is mein ye bhi kaha : phir us (dajjal) ne kaha : agar mujhey nikalney ki ijazat di gaee to main taiba (Madina) ke siwa tamam shehron mein jaunga, phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) un  (hazrat Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu)) ko logon ke samney le gaey aur (unki maujoodgi mein) aap ne un (logon) ke samney (ye waqia) bayan kiya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye taiba hai aur wo (shakhs) dajjal hai."
7389,"abu Zinad ne Shabi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Fatima binte-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par raunaq afroz huey aur farmaya : logo ! mujhey Tameem daari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye bataya hai ke unki qaum ke kuchh log apne aik jahaz mein samandar mein they, wo jahaz toot gaya aur unmein se kuchh log jahaz ke takhton mein se aik takhtey par Sawar ho gaey aur samandar mein aik jazeerey ki taraf ja nikley aur phir (aagey baqi bachi) hadis bayan ki."
7390,"ibne-Umar auzaye ne Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Makka aur Madina ke alawa koi Shahar nahi magar dajjal ! usey raundey ga. un (do shehron) ke raston mein se har rastey par Farishtey saf baandhtey huey pahra de rahe hongey phir wo aik shoreeli zamin mein utrey ga. us waqt Madina teen baar larazey ga aur har kaafir aur munafiq ismein se nikal kar us (dajjal) ke paas chala jaeyga."
7391,"Hammaad-bin-Salma ne Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, iske baad usi (pichhli hadis ki) tarah bayan kiya, magar usmein kaha : chunanche wo (dajjal) jurf ki shoreeli zamin mein aa kar apna khema lagaey ga aur kaha : har munafiq mard aur aurat nikal kar uske paas chaley jaengey."
7392,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : isbahaan ke yahudiyon mein se sattar (70) hazaar (yahudi) dajjal ki pairwi karengey, un (ke jismon) par tailsaan ki abaaein (chaadrein) hongi ."
7393,"Hujjaj-bin-Muhammad ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke mujhey abu-Zubair ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke mujhey umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : log dajjal se faraar ho kar pahadon mein jaengey. Hazrat umme-Sharik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke rasool ! us waqt Arab kahan hongey? (jo Deen ke difaa' mein seena-siper ho jatey hain) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo bahut kam hongey."
7394,abu-Aasim ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
7395,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Mukhtar ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne Humaid-bin-Hilal se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne aik giroh se riwayat ki jin mein abu-dahma aur abu-Qatada shamil huein, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Hisham-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzar kar Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jaya kartey they, aik din unhon-ne kaha : tum mujhey chhod kar aisey logon ke paas jatey ho jo mujh se zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hone-waale nahi they aur na unko mujh se zyada Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadison ka ilm hai, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna tha : Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) se lekar qiyamat tak koi makhlooq (fitna aur fasaad mein) aisi nahi jo dajjal se badi ho."
7396,"Ubaidullaah-bin-Amr ne Ayub se, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Hilal se aur unhon-ne apni qaum ke teen logon se riwayat ki jin mein abu Qatada bhi shamil hain ke ham Hisham-bin-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzar kar Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas jatey they. jis tarah Abdul-Azeez-bin-Mukhtar ki riwayat hai magar unhon-ne kaha : dajjal (ke fitney) se bada koi mamla (pesh nahi aaya)."
7397,"Alaa ke walid (Abdur-Rehman) ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chh (6) chizon ke zuhoor se pahley nek amal karne mein sabqat karo. suraj ke maghrib se tuloo honey, dhuein , dajjal , zamin ke chaupaaey , khas taur par tum mein se kisi aik ko pesh aaney waley mamley ( bimari , aajiz kar deney wala budhapa ya koi rukawat) aur har kisi ko pesh aaney wala mamla. ( maslan : ijtimaaii gumrahi, fitney ke zamaney mein qatle-aam, qiyamat se pahley.)"
7398,"Shoba ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hasan se, unhon-ne Ziyad-bin-riyah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chh (6) chizon ke zuhoor se pahley nek aamal mein sabqat karo : dajjal , dhuaan , zamin ka chaupaaya , suraj ka maghrib se tuloo hona, aam logon ke sath pesh aaney wala mamla ya khususi taur par tum se kisi aik ko pesh aaney wala mamla."
7399,Hammam ne Qatada se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
7400,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne hamein hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne khabar di, unhon-ne Mualla-bin-Ziyad se, unhon-ne Muawiya-bin-Qurra se, unhon-ne Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, isi tarah hamein Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne yahi hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha, hamein Hammad ne Mualla-bin-Ziyad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne is riwayat ko Muawiya bin-Qurra ki taraf lautaaya, unhon-ne Hazrat Ma'qil-bin-Yasaar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki taraf mansub kartey huey bayan kiya ke aap ne farmaya : har taraf phaili hui qatl aur ghaarat giri ke dauran mein ibadat (par tawajjoh markooz) karnaa, meri taraf hijrat karne ki tarah hai."
7401,"yahi hadis mujhey abu-Kamil ne bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
7402,"Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : qiyamat sirf badtareen logon par hi qaaim hogi."
7403,"Yaqoob ne abu-Hazim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap angoothey ke sath wali (shahadat ki ungli) aur badi ungli ke sath ishara kartey huey farma rahe they : main aur qiyamat is tarah (saath-saath) bhejey gaey hain."
7404,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada ko suna, kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey aur qiyamat ko in (shahadat aur badi ungliyon) ki tarah (saath-saath) maboos kiya (bheja) gaya hai. Shoba ne kaha : aur maine Qatada se unke hadis bayan karne ke doran mein suna : jitni unmein se aik ungli dusri se badi hai) itney se zamaney ka farq hai) mujhey malum nahi ye (mana) unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se naql kartey huey bayan kiya ya khud Qatada ne bayan kiya."
7405,"Khalid-bin-Haaris ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Qatada aur abu Tayyah ko hadis bayan kartey huey suna, un donon ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo hadis bayan kar rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey aur qiyamat ko is tarah maboos kiya (bheja) gaya hai. aur Shoba ne usey bayan kartey huey apni angusht shahadat aur darmyani ungli ko milaya."
7406,"Muaz aur Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Tayyah se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki."
7407,"ibne-abi Adi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Hamza zabi aur abu-Tayyah se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se un sab ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
7408,"Mabad ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey aur qiyamat ko is tarah bheja gaya hai. kaha : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne angusht shahadat aur darmyani ungli ko ikattha kiya."
7409,Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai kaha : dehaati log (baddoo log) jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aatey to aap se qiyamat ke mutaalliq sawal kartey ke qiyamat Kab aaeygi? aap unmein sabse kam Umr insan ki taraf dekh kar farmatey : agar ye zinda raha to ye boodha nahi hua hoga ke tum par tumhari (qiyamat ki) ghadi aa jaeygi.
7410,Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kiya : qiyamat Kab qaaim hogi? aur uske paas Ansar mein se aik ladka betha tha jisey Muhammad kaha jata tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar ye ladka zinda raha to shayad usey budhapa na pahunchega ke (tumhari) qiyamat aa jaeygi.
7411,"Maabad-bin-Hilal Anzi ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kiya : qiyamat Kab qaaim hogi ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) thodi der khamosh rahe, phir aap ne apne samney baithey azde-shanoo', ke aik ladkey ki taraf nazar ki, phir farmaya : agar ye ladka lambi umr pa gaya to usey budhapa nahi aaya hoga ke (tumhari) qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi. (Mabad ne) kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo ladka us din mera ham umr tha."
7412,"Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : (us waqt) Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ladka guzra jo mere ham umaron mein se tha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar isko mohlat mili to isey budhapa nahi aaya hoga ke (tum par) qiyamat aa jaeygi."
7413,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne iska silsile Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat aaeygi to aik aadmi ontni ka doodh nikal raha hoga wo bartan uske munh tak na pahuncha hoga ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi aur do aadmi kapdey ka saudaa kar rahe hongey unhon-ne khareedo-farokht (mukammal) nahi ki hogi ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi, aik shakhs apne hauz mein lipaai kar raha hoga wo bahar nahi nikal paya hoga ke qiyamat qaaim ho jaeygi."
7414,"Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do baar Saur phoonkney ke darmyan chalis (40) ka waqfa hoga. unhon (logon) ne kaha, Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) chalis (40) din? unhon-ne kaha : main inkar karta hun. logon ne kaha : chalis (40) mahiney? unhon-ne kaha : main inkar karta hun. logon ne kaha chalis (40) saal? unhon-ne kaha : main inkar karta hun. phir Allah Taala aasman se pani nazil farmaeyga to log isi tarah ugein gey jis tarah sabza ugtaa hai. unhon-ne kaha : aur insan ka koi hissey nahi, magar wo boseeda ho jaeyga, siwaey aik haddi ke wo damchi ki haddi ka aakhiri hissa hai qiyamat ke din usi se khilqat ki tarkeeb mukammal hogi."
7415,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : damchi ki haddi ke aakhiri sirey ke siwa poorey ibne-Aadam (ke jism) ko mitti kha leygi. usi se insan paida kiya gaya aur usi (aakhiri sirey) se phir (usey jod kar) ikattha kiya jaeyga.
7416,"Mamar ne Hammam-bin-Munabba se hadis bayan ki, kaha : ye hadisein hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kai hadisein zikr kin, unmein se (eik ye) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : insan ke jism mein aik haddi hai jis ko mitti kabhi na kha sakey gi, usi mein (se) qiyamat ke din usko poora bnaya jaeyga unhon (logon) ne puchha : Allah ke rasool ! wo kon si haddi hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo dam ki haddi ka aakhiri sira hey."
